estions%20and%20write%20unbiased%20product%20reviews%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fpersonal-finance-editorial-standards%23rating-credit-cards%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere's%20how%20we%20assess%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E).%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20we%20receive%20a%20commission%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Four-partners%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eour%20partners%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20however%2C%20our%20opinions%20are%20our%20own.%20Terms%20apply%20to%20offers%20listed%20on%20this%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20is%20perfect%20for%20infrequent%20Southwest%20travelers%20who%20want%20some%20benefits%20with%20this%20airline%20without%20paying%20a%20high%20annual%20fee.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20Overview%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EChase%20issues%20five%20different%20Southwest%20credit%20cards%3A%20Three%20consumer%20cards%2C%20and%20two%20business%20cards.%20The%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20is%20the%20entry-level%20version%2C%20with%20the%20lowest%20annual%20fee%20(%2469)%20of%20the%20bunch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20low%20annual%20fee%20on%20the%20Southwest%20Plus%20means%20you'll%20receive%20relatively%20few%20ongoing%20benefits%20beyond%20the%20current%20welcome%20bonus.%20This%20won't%20be%20an%20issue%20if%20you're%20just%20an%20occasional%20Southwest%20traveler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Southwest%20frequent%20flyers%20could%20get%20better%20value%20from%20the%20additional%20perks%20on%20other%20Southwest%20credit%20cards.%20The%20great%20thing%20about%20Southwest%20points%20is%20that%20they%20never%20expire%2C%20so%20there's%20no%20pressure%20to%20redeem%20your%20points%20immediately.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20way%20to%20redeem%20your%20points%20is%20for%20free%20flights%2C%20valued%20around%201.4%20cents%20per%20point%2C%20based%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-are-points-miles-worth-value%5C%22%3Epoints%20and%20miles%20valuations%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Rewards%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20Rewards%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESouthwest%20Plus%20Welcome%20Bonus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Plus%20card%20offers%20the%2050%2C000%20bonus%20points%20after%20you%20spend%20%241%2C000%20on%20purchases%20in%20the%20first%20three%20months%20from%20account%20opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Earn%20Points%20With%20the%20Southwest%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20earn%20rewards%20at%20the%20following%20rates%20on%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20points%20on%20Southwest%20purchases%20(including%20flights%2C%20inflight%20purchases%2C%20Southwest%20gift%20cards%2C%20and%20Southwest%20Vacations%20packages)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20points%20on%20Rapid%20Rewards%20hotel%20and%20car%20rental%20partner%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20points%20on%20local%20transit%20and%20commuting%2C%20including%20rideshare%20(and%20also%20passenger%20trains%2C%20buses%2C%20taxis%2C%20limousines%2C%20rideshare%2C%20ferries%2C%20toll%20bridges%20and%20highways%2C%20and%20parking%20lots%20and%20garages)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20points%20on%20internet%2C%20cable%2C%20phone%20services%2C%20and%20select%20streaming%20(Apple%20Music%2C%20Apple%20TV%2C%20Disney%2B%2C%20ESPN%2B%2C%20Fubo%20TV%2C%20HBO%20Max%2C%20Hulu%2C%20Netflix%2C%20Pandora%2C%20Paramount%2B%2C%20Peacock%2C%20Showtime%2C%20SiriusXM%2C%20Sling%2C%20Spotify%2C%20YouTube%20Premium%2C%20YouTube%20TV%2C%20and%20Vudu)%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E1x%20point%20on%20everything%20else%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20to%20Use%20Points%20From%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20Card%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20has%20an%20expansive%20domestic%20route%20network%20(including%20Hawaii)%20and%20also%20flies%20to%20a%20number%20of%20international%20destinations%20in%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Central%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESouthwest%20doesn't%20publish%20an%20award%20chart%20like%20some%20other%20airlines%20do.%20Instead%2C%20the%20number%20of%20points%20required%20for%20an%20award%20flight%20is%20tied%20to%20the%20price%20of%20a%20paid%20ticket.%20Based%20on%20Business%20Insider's%20points%20and%20miles%20valuations%2C%20you%20can%20expect%20to%20get%20an%20average%20value%20of%201.4%20cents%20per%20Southwest%20point%20when%20you%20redeem%20them%20for%20award%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-to-earn-redeem-southwest-points%5C%22%3ERedeeming%20Southwest%20points%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20book%20award%20flights%20online%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20once%20you%20log%20into%20your%20Rapid%20Rewards%20account%2C%20search%20for%20flights%20just%20as%20you%20would%20if%20you%20were%20looking%20for%20a%20paid%20ticket.%20The%20website%20allows%20you%20to%20toggle%20between%20the%20cash%20price%20and%20the%20points%20cost%20so%20you%20can%20easily%20compare%20the%20two.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20flying%20Southwest%20right%20now%2C%20there's%20no%20harm%20in%20holding%20on%20to%20your%20points%20until%20you're%20ready%2C%20because%20they'll%20never%20expire.%20However%2C%20Southwest%20credit%20card%20holders%20do%20have%20other%20options%20for%20redeeming%20points%20through%20the%20More%20Rewards%20program%2C%20including%20merchandise%2C%20gift%20cards%2C%20car%20rentals%2C%20hotels%2C%20cruises%2C%20and%20experiences.%20The%20value%20you'll%20get%20per%20point%20varies%2C%20but%20it's%20typically%20much%20lower%20than%20what%20you'd%20get%20if%20you%20redeemed%20for%20Southwest%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Benefits%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20Benefits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Plus%20Credit%20Card%20doesn't%20come%20with%20some%20of%20the%20other%20benefits%20offered%20by%20other%20Southwest%20cards%2C%20such%20as%20elite-qualifying%20points%20or%20travel%20credits.%20But%20you'll%20still%20get%20a%20variety%20of%20travel%20and%20purchase%20protections%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20handful%20of%20other%20perks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarn%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-companion-pass%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20Companion%20Pass%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20deals%20in%20travel%2C%20particularly%20for%20travelers%20who%20book%20a%20lot%20of%20flights%20around%20the%20US%2C%20Mexico%2C%20the%20Caribbean%2C%20and%20Central%20America.%20With%20the%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20you%20can%20bring%20a%20companion%20on%20any%20paid%20or%20award%20flights%20for%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20taxes%20and%20fees%20%E2%80%93%20typically%20%245.60%20one%20way%20on%20most%20domestic%20flights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEarlyBird%20Check-In%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECardholders%20receive%20two%20EarlyBird%20Check-Ins%20per%20account%20anniversary%20year%2C%20awarded%20as%20a%20statement%20credit%20after%20your%20purchase.%20EarlyBird%20Check-In%20normally%20costs%20%2415%20to%20%2425%20each%20way%2C%20and%20allows%20you%20to%20automatically%20check%20in%20for%20your%20flight%2036%20hours%20prior%20to%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20Southwest%20determines%20your%20boarding%20position%20by%20the%20time%20you%20check%20in%2C%20this%20feature%20can%20help%20you%20get%20on%20the%20airplane%20sooner%20and%20have%20a%20better%20opportunity%20to%20select%20your%20desired%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAnniversary%20Points%20Bonus%3C%