li%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ETraveling%20can%20be%20a%20great%20adventure%2C%20but%20it's%20even%20better%20with%20a%20friend%20or%20loved%20one.%20Southwest%20offers%20an%20incredible%20perk%20called%20the%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20arguably%20one%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20benefits%20in%20the%20travel%20industry.%20This%20benefit%20allows%20you%20to%20fly%20a%20buddy%20with%20you%20on%20any%20flight%20you%20take%20%E2%80%94%20with%20a%20few%20caveats%20and%20exceptions%2C%20of%20course.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20everything%20you%20need%20to%20know%20about%20getting%20and%20using%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20including%20the%20best%20strategies%20to%20keep%20it%20for%20as%20long%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ESouthwest%20Companion%20Pass%20Guide%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20allows%20you%20to%20choose%20one%20person%20to%20fly%20with%20you%20on%20both%20paid%20and%20award%20tickets%20for%20just%20the%20cost%20of%20taxes%20and%20fees%2C%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years%20(provided%20your%20timing%20is%20right).%20To%20earn%20the%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20you'll%20either%20have%20to%20accrue%20135%2C000%20qualifying%20points%20or%20fly%20100%20eligible%20one-way%20flights%20in%20a%20calendar%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20here's%20a%20nice%20little%20trick%3A%20The%20points%20you'll%20earn%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fsouthwest-companion-pass%5C%22%3ESouthwest%20credit%20card%3C%2Fa%3E%20bonuses%20and%20spending%20count%20toward%20earning%20the%20Companion%20Pass%20%E2%80%94%20so%20opening%20a%20card%20and%20earning%20the%20bonus%20is%20an%20easy%20way%20to%20achieve%20a%20big%20part%20of%20the%20requirement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%20allows%20you%20to%20book%20a%20friend%20or%20family%20member's%20airplane%20ticket%2C%20on%20the%20same%20flight%20as%20you%2C%20without%20needing%20to%20pay%20any%20cash%20or%20points%20for%20the%20flight.%20You%20will%20be%20responsible%20for%20taxes%20and%20fees%2C%20but%20typically%20these%20do%20not%20amount%20to%20much%20(about%20%246%20each%20way%20for%20a%20domestic%20flight).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20earn%20the%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20you%20can%20designate%20your%20travel%20companion%20in%20the%20Southwest%20system.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20that%20you%20can%20change%20to%20a%20different%20companion%20up%20to%20three%20times%20per%20calendar%20year.%20This%20means%20that%20you%20can%20bring%20along%20different%20friends%20for%20different%20trips.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20Get%20a%20Southwest%20Companion%20Pass%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20qualify%20for%20the%20Companion%20Pass%2C%20you%20need%20to%20earn%20135%2C000%20Companion%20Pass%20qualifying%20points%20or%20fly%20100%20one-way%20flights%20per%20calendar%20year%20on%20Southwest%20Airlines%2C%20which%20must%20be%20earned%20and%20posted%20to%20your%20Rapid%20Rewards%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20if%20you%20hold%20a%20Southwest%20credit%20card%2C%20you'll%20receive%20a%20%26quot%3Bboost%26quot%3B%20of%2010%2C000%20Companion%20Pass%20qualifying%20points%20each%20year.%20You%20won't%20actually%20receive%2010%2C000%20redeemable%20points%20%E2%80%94%20this%20benefit%20effectively%20reduces%20the%20number%20of%20points%20you%20must%20collect%20to%20125%2C000.%20You'll%20only%20receive%20one%20boost%20yearly%2C%20even%20if%20you%20have%20multiple%20Southwest%20cards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can%20earn%20qualifying%20points%20by%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBooking%20flights%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEarning%20points%20issued%20on%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%20credit%20cards%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEarning%20points%20from%20Rapid%20Rewards%20partners%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20won't%20earn%20qualifying%20points%20for%20the%20following%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPurchased%20points%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPoints%20transferred%20between%20Rapid%20Rewards%20members