00%20Companion%20Pass%20qualifying%20points%20every%20year%2C%20which%20gives%20you%20a%20head%20start%20on%20earning%20your%20next%20Companion%20Pass.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELearn%20more%20about%20this%20card%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fchase-southwest-rapid-rewards-premier-credit-card-review%5C%22%3EChase%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%20Premier%20credit%20card%20review%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3ESouthwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Priority%20Credit%20Card%20is%20Southwest's%20top-tier%20consumer%20credit%20card%2C%20and%20a%20great%20option%20for%20frequent%20Southwest%20travelers%20to%20keep%20in%20their%20wallet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20earning%20rates%20on%20the%20Priority%20card%20mirror%20those%20of%20the%20Southwest%20Rapid%20Rewards%C2%AE%20Premier%20Credit%20Card.%20Priority%20cardholders%20earn%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E3x%20on%20Southwest%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20on%20Rapid%20Rewards%20hotel%20and%20car%20rental%20partner%20purchases%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20on%20local%20transit%20and%20commuting%2C%20including%20rideshare%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E2x%20on%20internet%2C%20cable%2C%20phone%20services%2C%20and%20select%20streaming%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E1%20point%20per%20dollar%20on%20everything%20else%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20receive%207%2C500%20Rapid%20Rewards%20points%20on%20your%20card%20anniversary%2C%20earn%20tier-qualifying%20points%20toward%20A-List%20elite%20status%20when%20you%20spend%20money%20on%20this%20card%2C%20and%20receive%20a%20%2475%20annual%20Southwest%20travel%20credit%20as%20well%20as%20four%20upgraded%20boardings%20per%20year%20when%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Priority%20card%20also%20gives%20you%2025%25%20back%20on%20inflight%20drinks%20and%20WiFi%2C%20and%20a%20boost%20of%2010%2C000%20Companion%20Pass%20qualifying%20points%20each