0of%20applying%20and%20getting%20approved%20for%20a%20mortgage%20easy%20to%20understand%20and%20user%20friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20its%20offerings%20won't%20meet%20every%20borrower's%20needs.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20less%20common%20type%20of%20mortgage%20or%20you%20have%20a%20rocky%20credit%20history%2C%20you'll%20probably%20want%20to%20look%20elsewhere.%20Rocket's%20rates%20and%20fees%20are%20also%20right%20around%20average%2C%20and%20it's%20possible%20another%20lender%20could%20offer%20you%20a%20more%20affordable%20loan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ERocket%20Mortgage%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EDoes%20Rocket%20Mortgage%20have%20a%20good%20reputation%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERocket%20Mortgage%20has%20a%20reputation%20for%20providing%20good%20customer%20service%20and%20a%20convenient%20application%20process.%20The%20company%20has%20strong%20customer%20reviews%2C%20so%20you%20may%20like%20it%20if%20customer%20support%20is%20a%20high%20priority.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhy%20not%20go%20with%20Rocket%20Mortgage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lender%20doesn't%20offer%20certain%20types%20of%20mortgages%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fusda-loan%5C%22%3EUSDA%20loans%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20doesn't%20have%20physical%20locations%2C%20so%20if%20you%20want%20to%20walk%20into%20a%20branch%20to%20speak%20with%20someone%20in%20person%2C%20you're%20better%20off%20using%20a%20different%20lender.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20bank%20is%20behind%20Rocket%20Mortgage%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERocket%20Mortgage%2C%20formerly%20known%20as%20Quicken%20Loans%2C%20is%20a%20part%20of%20Rocket%20Companies.%20It%20was%20founded%20in%201985%20by%20Dan%20Gilbert.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIs%20Rocket%20Mortgage%20legit%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20Rocket%20Mortgage%20is%20a%20real%20mortgage%20lender%20that's%20licensed%20to%20lend%20in%20all%2050%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20does%20Rocket%20Mortgage's%20application%