s%20some%20folks%20may%20prefer%20to%20wear%20a%20rubber%20strap%20while%20others%20may%20like%20the%20look%20and%20feel%20of%20woven%20nylon.%20Deciding%20between%20the%20two%20comes%20down%20to%20which%20one%20you%20feel%20is%20more%20comfortable%20against%20your%20skin%20while%20wearing%20it%20normally%20and%20while%20working%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20a%20rubber%20strap%20may%20be%20a%20bit%20easier%20to%20clean%20as%20it%20won't%20need%20as%20much%20time%20to%20dry%20off%20as%20a%20nylon%20band%20would.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20Apple%20Watch%20band%20for%20runners%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20subjective%20based%20on%20personal%20preference%20and%20comfort%2C%20some%20Apple%20Watch%20sport%20bands%20are%20better%20than%20others%20for%20running%2C%20particularly%20those%20made%20of%20rubber%20with%20a%20design%20that%20promotes%20airflow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20Nike%20Sport%20Band%20features%20a%20perforated%20design%20that%20helps%20keep%20the%20watch%20lightweight%20and%20breathable%2C%20two%20things%20that%20are%20vital%20to%20runners%20(especially%20those%20covering%20long%20distances).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20Apple-branded%20sports%20bands%20better%20than%20third-party%20options%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20necessarily.%20So%20long%20as%20the%20third-party%20option%20comes%20from%20a%20reputable%20brand%20like%20Nike%2C%20Nomad%2C%20Otterbox%2C%20or%20others.%20Apple-branded%20sports%20bands%20are%20premium%20bands%2C%20but%20they%20aren't%20the%20only%20option%20you%20have%20when%20picking%20out%20one%20of%20the%20best%20Apple%20Watch%20bands%20for%20working%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20best%20material%20for%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20sports%20band%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20materials%20to%20look%20for%20when%20shopping%20for%20an%20Apple%20Watch%20band%20for%20working%20out%20are%20either%20rubbe