ey%2C%20a%20CFP%C2%AE%20professional%20and%20the%20host%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%22f577667779d98161a3b970b0399d9601%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2240%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fillumintfc.com%2F%5C%22%20data-saferedirecturl%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fq%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fbykevinmahoney.com%2F%26amp%3Bsource%3Dgmail%26amp%3Bust%3D1656165049473000%26amp%3Busg%3DAOvVaw1ydEj5hMlfttQq3PIrPtZJ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFinancially%20Well%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20finance%20podcast%20for%20Millennials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBuilding%20a%20CD%20ladder%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ECD%20laddering%20is%20also%20often%20used%20as%20a%20strategy%20if%20you%20want%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20competitive%20interest%20rates%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20deposit%20all%20your%20money%20in%20a%20specific%20term.%20With%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcd-ladder-what-is-it-how-does-it-work%5C%22%3ECD%20ladder%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'll%20open%20multiple%20CDs%20of%20different%20terms.%20For%20example%2C%20you%20can%20open%20a%201-year%20CD%2C%202-year%2C%20and%203-year%20CD%20at%20all%20once%2C%20and%20split%20your%20money%20between%20these%20three%20CDs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20primary%20benefits%20of%20creating%20a%20CD%20ladder%20is%20that%20it%20offers%20more%20flexibility.%20For%20example%2C%20if%20interest%20rates%20on%20CDs%20go%20up%2C%20you%20may%20be%20able%20to%20take%20advantage%20of%20higher%20rates%20once%20your%20shorter-term%20CDs%20mature.%20If%20you%20need%20access%20to%20your%20money%20sooner%20than%20you%20anticipated%20or%20worry%20about%20early%20withdrawal%20penalties%2C%20CD%20ladders%20may%20also%20be%20helpful%20because%20you'll%20be%20able%20to%20access%20a%20part%20of%20your%20savings%20once%20each%20term%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Steps%20to%20open%20a%20CD%20account%5C%22%3ESteps%20to%20open%20a%20CD%20account%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECompare%20different%20banks%20and%20credit%20unions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESelecting%20the%20right%20financial%20institution%20can%20also%20make%20a%20big%20difference%20in%20getting%20strong%20CDs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnline%20banks%20or%20credit%20unions%20will%20usually%20offer%20the%20highest%20CD%20rates.%20Meanwhile%2C%20national%20banks%20usually%20offer%20low%20interest%20rates%20that%20are%20either%20on%20par%20with%20or%20lower%20than%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Faverage-bank-interest-rates%5C%22%3Eaverage%20CD%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EPreparing%20necessary%20documentation%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you've%20narrowed%20down%20your%20preferences%20and%20found%20a%20strong%20CD%20option%2C%20you%20can%20generally%20open%20an%20account%20online%20or%20at%20a%20branch.%20Generally%2C%20when%20opening%20a%20bank%20account%2C%20you'll%20need%20the%20following%20information%20and%20documents%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBasic%20information%20like%20your%20legal%20name%2C%20address%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20phone%20number%2C%20or%20email%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGovernment-issued%20ID%20like%20a%20driver's%20license%20or%20passport%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESocial%20Security%20number%20or%20individual%20tax%20identification%20number%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20do%20not%20have%20a%20government-issued%20ID%2C%20there%20are%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanks-credit-unions-for-immigrants-non-us-citizens%5C%22%3Ebanks%20and%20credit%20unions%20that%20make%20it%20easy%20for%20immigrants%20and%20non-US%20citizens%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20open%20a%20bank%20account.%20At%20these%20banks%2C%20you%20can%20use%20a%20foreign%20passport%20or%20foreign%20ID%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EMaking%20an%20initial%20deposit%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20want%20to%20keep%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20minimum%20amount%20needed%20to%20open%20a%20CD.%20The%20minimum%20opening%20deposit%20varies%20from%20bank%20to%20bank.%20Some%20financial%20institutions%20will%20let%20you%20open%20an%20account%20with%20%240%2C%20but%20generally%2C%20at%20least%20%241%2C000%20is%20needed%20to%20get%20a%20CD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20know%20before%20opening%20a%20CD%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20to%20know%20before%20opening%20a%20CD%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EReview%20CD%20early%20withdrawal%20penalties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20CDs%20do%20not%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmonthly-bank-maintenance-fee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emonthly%20service%20fees%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20standard%20savings%20accounts%20or%20money%20market%20accounts%2C%20you%20do%20want%20to%20be%20mindful%20of%20early%20withdrawal%20penalties.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcd-early-withdrawal-penalties%5C%22%3Eearly%20withdrawal%20penalty%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20fee%20for%20withdrawing%20money%20from%20your%20account%20before%20the%20maturity%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20earn%20the%20rate%20that%20the%20CDs%20are%20offering%2C%20you%20have%20to%20keep%20it%20in%20that%20CD%20for%20a%20certain%20amount%20of%20time.%20I%20think%20that's%20the%20variable%20that's%20most%20likely%20to%20trip%20people%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mahoney.%20%26quot%3BThose%20numbers%20can%20be%20very%20appealing%20on%20the%20surface%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20think%20through%20when%20you're%20going%20to%20need%20the%20money%20and%20whether%20the%20terms%20of%20any%20particular%20CD%20actually%20work%20for%20your%20circumstances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20what%20happens%20when%20a%20CD%20matures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20also%20want%20to%20consider%20what%20happens%20when%20a%20CD%20matures.%20For%20example%2C%20does%20your%20CD%20automatically%20renew%3F%20If%20it%20does%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20see%20how%20long%20the%20grace%20period%20is%20for%20making%20changes%20to%20the%20account%20before%20it%20renews.%20During%20the%20grace%20period%2C%20you%20can%20withdraw%20any%20amount%20of%20money%20from%20a%20CD%20without%20facing%20penalties.%20You%20may%20also%20choose%20to%20deposit%20more%20money%20into%20a%20CD%20and%20let%20it%20renew%20for%20another%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20also%20want%20to%20know%20the%20process%20for%20closing%20a%20CD%20at%20a%20financial%20institution.%20Some%20banks%20let%20you%20close%20a%20CD%20online%2C%20while%20others%20may%20require%20you%20to%20call%20customer%20support%20instead.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3ECD%20opening%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%26quot%3Blist%26quot%3B%2C%7B%7D%2C%26quot%3Blist_item%26quot%3B%2C%7B%26quot%3Bindent%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Btype%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bnumbered%26quot%3B%7D%5D%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20do%20I%20need%20to%20open%20a%20CD%20account%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20open%20a%20CD%2C%20you'll%20need%20two%20forms%20of%20government-issued%20IDs%20and%20your%20social%20security%20number%20or%20ITIN%20number.%20You'll%20also%20provide%20basic%20information%20like%20your%20legal%20name%2C%20home%20address%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20phone%20number%2C%20or%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-pm-slice%3D%5C%221%201%20%5B%26quot%3Blist%26quot%3B%2C%7B%7D%2C%26quot%3Blist_item%26quot%3B%2C%7B%26quot%3Bindent%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Btype%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3Bnumbered%26quot%3B%7D%5D%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20I%20add%20more%20money%20to%20my%20CD%20later%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20only%20add%20money%20to%20add-on%20CDs%20while%20they%20are%20open.%20Traditional%20CDs%2C%20no-penalty%20CDs%2C%20bump-up%20CDs%2C%20and%20step-up%20CDs%2