20far%2C%20the%20party%20has%20named%20267%20candidates%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20nearly%2021%25%20of%20sitting%20MPs%20have%20already%20not%20been%20repeated%20from%20their%20respective%20constituencies.%20The%20strategy%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20has%20been%20designed%20keeping%20possible%20anti-incumbency%20in%20mind%2C%20and%20the%20decisions%20have%20been%20based%20on%20the%20feedback%20the%20party%20has%20got%20from%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20choice%20of%20candidates%20is%20also%20important%20given%20the%20party's%20target%20of%20winning%20370%20seats%20on%20its%20own%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20due%20in%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20from%20now%2C%20which%20will%20entail%20getting%2067%20more%20constituencies%20than%20it%20did%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20first%20list%2C%20released%20on%20March%202%2C%20saw%20only%2033%20MPs%20-%20including%20Pragya%20Thakur.%20Ramesh%20Bidhuri%20and%20Parvesh%20Verma%20-%20being%20replaced%20despite%20195%20candidates%20being%20named%2C%2030%20MPs%20were%20shown%20the%20door%20in%20Wednesday's%20list%20of%2072%20names.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20267%20names%20in%20the%20two%20lists%2C%20the%20number%20of%20sitting%20MPs%20repeated%20is%20high%2C%20at%20140%2C%20and%2067%20MPs%20have%20not%20been%20given%20tickets.%20Two%20of%20these%20MPs%2C%20including%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20-%20who%20has%20been%20replaced%20in%20East%20Delhi%20by%20Harsh%20Malhotra%20-%20had%20decided%20not%20to%20contest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENumbers%20Game%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20second%20list%2C%2020%20names%20each%20have%20been%20declared%20from%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20seven%20from%20Gujarat%2C%20six%20each%20from%20Telangana%20and%20Haryana%2C%20five%20from%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20two%20each%20from%20Delhi%2C%20Uttarakhand%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20one%20each%20from%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Delhi%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20replaced%20six%20of%20its%20sitting%20MPs%20and%20only%20one%2C%20Manoj%20Tiwari%2C%20has%20been%20repeated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2020%20candidates%20declared%20for%20Karnataka%20in%20the%20second%20list%2C%2011%20MPs%20have%20been%20replaced%20while%20only%20eight%20have%20been%20repeated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20in%20Maharashtra%20is%20the%20opposite%2C%20with%2014%20MPs%20being%20repeated%20and%20the%20tickets%20of%20only%20five%20getting%20cancelled.%20The%20MPs%20being%20repeated%20include%20Union%20Minister%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20from%20Nagpur%2C%20while%20Pritam%20Munde%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20her%20sister%2C%20Pankaja%20Munde%2C%20in%20Beed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Gujarat%2C%20in%20the%20second%20list%2C%20only%20three%20out%20of%20seven%20sitting%20MPs%20have%20been%20repeated.%20The%20omissions%20include%20Union%20Minister%20Darshana%20Jardosh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20replaced%20by%20Mukesh%20Dalal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20six%20candidates%20declared%20in%20Haryana%20in%20the%20second%20list%2C%20three%20sitting%20MPs%20have%20been%20repeated%20and%20two%20have%20been%20replaced.%20A%20new%20candidate%20has%20been%20named%20for%20a%20seat%20where%20the%20sitting%20MP%20died.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETelangana%2C%20where%20the%20BJP%20had%20won%20only%20four%20seats%20last%20time%2C%20has%20seen%20one%20MP%20being%20repeated%20and%20one%20ticket%20being%20cancelled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%20five%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20candidates%20declared%20in%20the%20second%20list%2C%20two%20MPs%20have%20been%20repeated%20and%20two%20omitted.%20A%20new%20candidate%2C%20Vivek%20Sahu%2C%20will%20be%20fielded%20against%20Nakul%20Nath%20in%20the%20Chhindwara%20constituency%2C%20which%20was%20the%20only%20seat%20the%20BJP%20had%20lost%20in%20the%20state%20in%202019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20MPs%20named%20for%20Himachal%20in%20the%20second%20list%20are%20getting%20a%20tick