around%20764%20square%20kilometres%20divided%20between%20the%20two%20countries%E2%80%99%20western%20and%20northern%20borders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChina%20also%20made%20an%20additional%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220126065424%2Fhttps%3A%2Fthewire.in%2Fexternal-affairs%2Fchina-bhutan-india-territory%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esurprising%20claim%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20the%20Sakteng%20wildlife%20sanctuary%20in%202020.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20direct%20bilateral%20border%20talks%20began%20in%201984%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20have%20held%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2Fbhutan-china-want-deal-on-boundaries-soon%2Farticle67455065.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E25%20rounds%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20boundary%20talks%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-china-set-up-technical-team-on-delimitation-of-boundary%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E13%20rounds%20of%20meetings%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20at%20the%20expert%20level.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%201997%2C%20China%20proposed%20a%20%E2%80%98package%20deal%E2%80%99%20offering%20to%20relinquish%20claims%20on%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20central%20areas%20in%20exchange%20for%20territory%20in%20its%20western%20part%2C%20including%20Doklam.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhutan%2C%20reportedly%20pressured%20by%20India%2C%20declined%20the%20offer%20due%20to%20concerns%20over%20China%E2%80%99s%20proximity%20to%20the%20narrow%20Siliguri%20corridor.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndian%20soldiers%2C%20acting%20on%20behalf%20of%20Bhutan%2C%20confronted%20Chinese%20troops%20constructing%20a%20road%20in%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20Doklam%20region%20near%20the%20tri-junction%20of%20the%20three%20countries%E2%80%99%20boundaries%20in%20June%202017.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20a%2073-day%20standoff%2C%20both%20Indian%20and%20Chinese%20troops%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20220126065424%2Fhttps%3A%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fdoklam-india-china-withdraw-troops-no-clarity-chinas-road-building-efforts%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewithdrew%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20subsequent%20satellite%20imagery%20has%20revealed%20Chinese%20construction%20of%20a%20network%20of%20military%20infrastructure%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20the%20end%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20there%20has%20been%20notable%20momentum%20in%20Bhutan%20towards%20the%20finalisation%20of%20its%20border%20negotiations%20with%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20informed%20observers%2C%20Thimpu%E2%80%99s%20proactive%20stance%20is%20driven%20by%20the%20acknowledgment%20that%20China%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fdiplomacy%2Farticle%2F3251394%2Fchinese-village-construction-disputed-zone-outpaces-china-bhutan-border-talks%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esalami%20slicing%E2%80%99%20tactics%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20along%20the%20border%20cannot%20be%20effectively%20halted%20due%20to%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20resources.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20October%202021%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20China%20signed%20a%20memorandum%20of%20understanding%20to%20expedite%20boundary%20talks%20with%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fkuenselonline.com%2Fbhutan-china-sign-mou-to-expedite-boundary-negotiations%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethree%20stage%20roadmap%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%20After%20the%20delimitation%20of%20the%20border%20on%20maps%2C%20it%20envisages%20joint%20surveys%20for%20demarcating%20the%20border.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%2025%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eth%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20round%20of%20boundary%20talks%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20agreed%20on%20the%20guidelines%20of%20the%20joint%20technical%20team%20that%20would%20delimit%20and%20demarcate%20the%20boundary.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20a%20meeting%20with%20Bhutan%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20minister%2C%20Chinese%20foreign%20minister%20Wang%20Yi%20said%20that%20Beijing%20was%20ready%20to%20conclude%20the%20process%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fchina-bhutan-vow-to-conclude-border-talks-soon-will-have-implications-for-india%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20soon%20as%20possible%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBhutan%E2%80%99s%20reluctance%20to%20authorise%20the%20Indian%20military%20road%20until%20the%20border%20with%20China%20is%20conclusively%20settled%20suggests%20that%20Thimphu%20is%20equally%20eager%20to%20conclude%20the%20matter%20without%20jeopardising%20the%20ongoing%20boundary%20negotiations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710354838000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F10134907%2F24309575841_545d70a37a_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-pm-india-vist-china-border-talks-shadow%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20has%20proposed%20connecting%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Assam%20with%20a%20motorable%20road%20through%20Bhutan.%20But%20it%20is%20understood%20that%20Bhutan's%20government%20is%20not%20keen%20on%20the%20proposal%20until%20its%20border%20with%20China%20is%20demarcated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fbhutan-pm-india-vist-china-border-talks-shadow%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22All%20Best%20Actress%20Oscar%20Winners%20in%20Academy%20Award%20History%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710