ollowed%20by%20claims%20that%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20has%20been%20sending%20it%20feelers.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20BJP%20apparently%20offered%20him%20just%20six%20seats%20--%20to%20be%20split%20with%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20--%20sources%20said%20the%20Opposition%20had%20offered%20LJP%20eight%20seats%2C%20all%20six%20it%20won%20in%202019%20and%20two%20more%20in%20neighbouring%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20as%20bonus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChirag%20Paswan%2C%20who%20recently%20claimed%20that%20%26quot%3BEvery%20Party%2C%20Every%20Coalition%20Wants%20Me%20To%20Be%20On%20Its%20Side%2C%26quot%3B%20settled%20for%20five%20seats%20today.%20But%20he%20made%20it%20clear%20after%20the%20meeting%20that%20his%20uncle%20Pashupati%20Paras%20would%20not%20be%20given%20any%20seat%20from%20his%20quota.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20sealing%20the%20deal%20is%20a%20huge%20plus%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20from%20a%20position%20of%20isolation%20imposed%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20defection%20to%20the%C2%A0%20Grand%20Alliance%2C%20has%20suddenly%20found%20itself%20rich%20with%20his%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20party%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20was%20second%20to%20none%20--%20the%20one%20extra%20seat%20marking%20it%20as%20the%20alpha%20in%20the%20alliance.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20JDU%2C%20after%20a%20silent%20and%20bitter%20face-off%2C%20had%20decided%20on%20a%2050%3A50%20formula%20and%20contested%20on%20an%20equal%20number%20of%20seats.%20The%20division%20was%2017%20seats%20each%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20Mr%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20and%20six%20for%20Lok%20Janashakti%20Party%2C%20then%20led%20by%20Chirag%20Paswan's%20father%20Ram%20Vilas%20Paswan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20had%20won%2039%20of%20the%2040%20seats%20--%20only%20one%20had%20gone%20to%20the%20Opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710354720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2Fk41hue