20Ambedkar's%20Party%26quot%3B%3A%20Sharad%20Pawar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20President%20Sharad%20Pawar%20on%20Wednesday%20said%20seat-sharing%20among%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20(MVA)%20constituents%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20is%20stuck%20as%20leaders%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20political%20outfit%20led%20by%20BR%20Ambedkar's%20grandson%20Prakash%20Ambedkar%20to%20join%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pawar%20maintained%20alliance%20leaders%20have%20suggested%20giving%20four%20to%20five%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20to%20the%20Prakash%20Ambedkar-led%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20(VBA)%2C%20which%2C%20he%20said%2C%20has%20given%20a%20list%20of%2016%20constituencies%20where%20it%20claims%20to%20have%20a%20good%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expressed%20confidence%20about%20finalising%20allocation%20of%20seats%20among%20MVA%20allies%2C%20which%20currently%20includes%20the%20Congress%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20and%20the%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%2C%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MVA%20is%20part%20of%20the%20national-level%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Ambedkar-led%20party%20did%20not%20win%20a%20single%20seat%20in%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20it%20garnered%20a%20healthy%2014%20per%20cent%20vote%20share%20and%20damaged%20prospects%20of%20candidates%20of%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20then-undivided%20NCP%20in%20several%20constituencies%2C%20according%20to%20political%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Nanded%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra%20and%20then%20Congress%20candidate%20Ashok%20Chavan%20lost%20the%20election%20by%20nearly%2040%2C000%20votes.%20The%20VBA%20candidate%20in%20Nanded%20had%20received%20more%20than%201%20lakh%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Ambedkar%20had%20then%20criticised%20the%20Congress%20for%20not%20accepting%20his%20offer%20to%20join%20hands%20with%20him%20and%20put%20up%20a%20challenge%20against%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20last%20two%20weeks%2C%20Mr%20Ambedkar%20and%20his%20colleagues%20have%20been%20claiming%20that%20MVA%20leaders%20are%20delaying%20finalisation%20of%20seat-sharing%20formula%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20has%2048%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%2C%20the%20second%20highest%20after%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20(80).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20this%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20waiting%20for%20the%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%20to%20come%20on%20board.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20come%20with%20us.%20Our%20seat-sharing%20formula%20is%20on%20hold%20for%20the%20VBA.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Union%20minister%20asserted%20that%20Mr%20Ambedkar%20has%20been%20talking%20about%20ousting%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20VBA%20has%20any%20genuine%20complaints%2C%20we%20are%20ready%20to%20take%20note%20and%20resolve%20them.%20We%20are%20also%20ready%20to%20take%20any%20corrective%20action.%20There%20is%20a%20need%20to%20bring%20unanimity%20at%20the%20state%20level.%20Prakash%20Ambedkar%20always%20says%20the%20Modi%20government%20should%20go.%20We%20agree%20with%20his%20line%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20finalise%20(seat-sharing)%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20days%20when%20issues%20related%20to%20VBA%20are%20resolved%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20number%20of%20constituencies%20the%20regional%20outfit%20is%20asking%20for%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMr%20Ambedkar%20gave%20a%20list%20of%2016%20seats%20where%20the%20VBA%20has%20a%20good%20presence.%20The%20VBA%20has%20asked%20MVA%20leaders%20how%20many%20seats%20they%20can%20share%20out%20of%20those%2016%20constituencies.%20We%20have%20suggested%20giving%20four%20to%20five%20seats%20to%20them.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%