Wangchuk%20on%20Day%208%20of%20His%20Climate%20Fast%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13231912%2FWangchuk-Sonam.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3EClimate%20activist%20and%20innovator%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%20is%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98climate%20fast%E2%80%99%20at%20Leh%20in%20Ladakh.%20The%20Ramon%20Magsaysay%20Award%20winner%20of%202017%20is%20on%20a%20hunger%20strike%20%E2%80%93%20a%20fast%20unto%20death%20%E2%80%93%20to%20demand%20special%20status%20and%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20virtual%20press%20conference%20from%20his%20protest%20site%20on%20Wednesday%20(March%2013)%2C%20Wangchuk%20highlighted%20why%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20(which%20gives%20states%20in%20hilly%20regions%20with%20a%20significant%20tribal%20population%20special%20administrative%20powers)%20in%20and%20statehood%20for%20Ladakh%20is%20crucial%20for%20its%20ecology%2C%20environment%20and%20indigenous%20peoples.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResponding%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20specific%20questions%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%20that%20the%20climate%20fast%20is%20about%20giving%20rights%20to%20local%20indigenous%20peoples%20in%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20administration%20because%20they%20will%20be%20more%20concerned%20about%20the%20next%20generation%20than%20a%20three-year%20term%20bureaucrat%20who%20has%20no%20idea%20about%20its%20distinct%20topography%2C%20environment%2C%20culture%20and%20linguistics%20would%20be.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CMaterial%20development%E2%80%9D%20that%20is%20limitless%20and%20disregards%20natural%20resources%20and%20indigenous%20people%2C%20wildlife%2C%20flora%20and%20fauna%20is%20not%20development%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20certain%20that%20the%20BJP%20will%20lose%20its%20votes%20and%20seat%20in%20Ladakh%20because%20people%20have%20lost%20faith%20in%20the%20party%20that%20went%20back%20on%20its%20promises%20to%20implement%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20twice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20innovator%20of%20ice%20stupa%20fame%20appealed%20to%20people%20across%20the%20country%20to%20join%20him%20on%20one%20day%20of%20his%2021-day%20fast%3A%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20citizens%20are%20responding%3A%20many%20plan%20to%20come%20together%20in%20silent%20gatherings%20to%20take%20the%20fast%20on%20Sunday%20and%20show%20solidarity%20with%20Ladakh%2C%20its%20people%20and%20its%20environment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAbout%20truth%2C%20environment%2C%20democracy%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference%20conducted%20by%20the%20environmental%20group%20Friends%20of%20Ladakh%20and%20Friends%20of%20Nature%20(FOLFON%2C%20which%20has%20been%20banded%20together%20to%20spread%20the%20word%20of%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20climate%20fast)%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Wangchuk%20first%20gave%20an%20introduction%20to%20his%20ongoing%2021-day%20climate%20fast%20at%20Leh%20in%20Ladakh.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EToday%20is%20day%20eight%20of%20his%20fast%20and%20he%20is%20surviving%20only%20on%20water%20and%20salt%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSAVELADAKH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SAVELADAKH%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FSAVEHIMALAYAS%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23SAVEHIMALAYAS%