%20and%20everything%20will%20be%20resolved%20sooner%20than%20that.%20But%20if%20not%20we%20are%20very%20much%20prepared%20for%20longer%20durations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWhy%20this%20fast%3F%20It%E2%80%99s%20about%20truth%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20%5Bthe%5D%20environment%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEven%20when%20Ladakh%20was%20with%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20for%20some%2070%20years%2C%20its%20people%20have%20always%20wanted%20to%20be%20an%20entity%20of%20their%20own%2C%20because%20it%20had%20always%20been%20an%20independent%20kingdom%20in%20the%20Himalayas%20like%20Sikkim%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20Tibet%2C%20said%20Wangchuk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20because%20Ladakh%E2%80%99s%20topography%2C%20environment%2C%20culture%20and%20linguistics%20have%20all%20been%20very%20different%20not%20just%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20India%2C%20but%20the%20world%20too.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Ladakh%20received%20the%20tag%20of%20a%20Union%20territory%20(UT)%20in%202019%20(%E2%80%9Cmuch%20to%20all%20our%20surprise%E2%80%9D%2C%20in%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20words)%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20were%20very%20grateful%20to%20the%20ruling%20party.%20But%20their%20%E2%80%9Cexpectation%20and%20demand%E2%80%9D%20had%20always%20been%20that%20they%20have%20a%20legislative%20assembly%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20means%20the%20democratic%20representation%20of%20people%20in%20an%20assembly%20which%20will%20then%20make%20laws%20and%20policies%20to%20manage%20the%20fragile%20ecosystems%20of%20these%20mountains%E2%80%9D%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20thing%20was%20about%20the%20safeguards%20of%20this%20especially%20fragile%20zone%2C%20and%20Article%20370%20provided%20that%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20were%20okay%20with%20%5BArticle%5D%20370%20going%20because%20only%20that%20could%20allow%20Ladakh%20to%20be%20a%20separate%20entity.%20We%20were%20okay%20about%20that%20for%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%A6%20of%20course%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20different%20case%20for%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%E2%80%9CNatural%20no-brainer%E2%80%9D%20but%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20deliver%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakh%20expected%20that%20its%20safeguards%20would%20come%20from%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20the%20climate%20activist%20said%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CBecause%20this%20%5Bschedule%5D%20is%20tailor-made%20for%20hilly%20regions%20with%20distinct%20indigenous%20tribal%20communities.%20And%20normally%2C%2050%25%20tribal%20population%20is%20enough%20to%20qualify%20for%20that%2C%20but%20Ladakh%20has%2097%25.%20So%20we%20were%20hands-down%20qualified%20for%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20commented.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20we%20had%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20government%20that%20was%20kind%20enough%20to%20make%20Ladakh%20a%20UT%20would%20also%20give%20us%20that.%20It%20was%20a%20natural%20no-brainer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20itself%20assured%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20again%20and%20again%20that%20this%20safeguard%20would%20be%20given%20to%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20they%20spoke%20in%20large%20gatherings%20about%20this%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-roots-of-discontent-in-ladakh%5C%22%3EThe%20Roots%20of%20Discontent%20in%20Ladakh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20even%20kept%20it%20in%20its%202019%20election%20manifesto%20%E2%80%93%20it%20was%20in%20fact%20one%20of%20the%20top%20three%20promises%20they%20made.%20(Behind%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20seat%20hung%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20manifesto%20in%20which%20the%20BJP%20promised%20to%20implement%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%20and%20the%20climate%20activist%20also%20pointed%20to%20it%20in%20between%20his%20address).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20people%20voted%20%E2%80%9Cheavily%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20party%20won%20from%20Ladakh.%20But%20the%20BJP%20didn%E2%80%99t%20keep%20their%20promise%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%20%E2%80%9CFor%20months%2C%20they%20went%20silent.%20They%20were%20even%20upset%20when%20we%20reminded%20them%20of%20this%20promise.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20even%20took%20police%20action%20against%20anybody%20who%20uttered%20the%20words%20%E2%80%9CSixth%20Schedule%E2%80%9D%2C%20despite%20it%20being%20a%20provision%20in%20the%20Indian%20constitution.%20So%20in%202020%2C%20Ladakhis%20decided%20to%20boycott%20the%20elections%20to%20the%20Hill%20Council%20of%20Leh%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20present%20government%20sent%20a%20special%20airplane%20to%20Leh%2C%20took%20Ladakhi%20leaders%20to%20Delhi%20and%20appealed%20to%20them%20to%20let%20the%20election%20proceed.%20The%20government%20promised%20they%20would%20%E2%80%9Csolve%20everything%E2%80%9D%20after%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20tribal%20indigenous%20leaders%20and%20people%20are%20very%20trusting%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said.%20So%20once%20again%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Ladakh%20%E2%80%9Cvoted%20heavily%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20BJP%20and%20they%20formed%20the%20government%20for%20the%20Ladakh%20Autonomous%20Hill%20Council.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETwo%20elections%20were%20thus%20won%20on%20this%20promise%20by%20the%20BJP%2C%20Wangchuk%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYet%20four%20years%20later%2C%20nothing%20has%20happened%2C%20he%20added.%20The%20home%20ministry%20kept%20%E2%80%9Cdilly-dallying%E2%80%9D%2C%20not%20taking%20decisions%2C%20giving%20several%20excuses%2C%20and%20so%20on%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Climate%20fast%20is%20now%20our%20only%20resort%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%20on%20March%204%2C%20they%20outright%20denied%20any%20possibility%20%5Bof%20this%5D%20and%20said%20that%20we%20cannot%20give%20you%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%2C%E2%80%9D%20Wangchuk%20said.%20A%20UT%20with%20legislature%20or%20statehood%20is%20also%20not%20possible%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhi%20people%2C%20therefore%2C%20%E2%80%9Care%20very%20hurt%E2%80%9D%20and%20our%20%E2%80%9Conly%20resort%E2%80%9D%20is%20to%20start%20a%20movement%2C%20Wangchuk%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20that%20not%20only%20people%20in%20Ladakh%20but%20all%20over%20the%20nation%20join%20us%20in%20the%20support%20and%20defence%20of%20truth%20and%20justice%20%E2%80%A6%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20about%20Ladakh.%20When%20somebody%20makes%20a%20promise%2C%20they%20must%20keep%20it%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20like%20giving%20a%20cheque%20which%20says%20Sixth%20Schedule%20and%20then%20you%20take%20it%20and%20it%20bounces.%20That%20should%20not%20be%20acceptable.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20should%20be%20punishable.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20are%20on%20a%20fast.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221007%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809.png%201007w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03180459%2Fimage-1809-300x130.png%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22435%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThousands%20of%20protesters%20rallied%20in%20Leh%20and%20Kargil%20districts%20of%20Ladakh%20on%20Saturday%2C%20February%203%2C%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20constitutional%20changes%20brought%20about%20by%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370.%20Photo%3A%20By%20Special%20Arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMore%20and%20more%20people%20are%20joining%20the%20fast%20in%20different%20days%2C%20Wangchuk%20said%2C%20showing%20a%20glimpse%20of%20the%20people%20gathered%20at%20the%20site%20sitting%20with%20him%20via%20his%20phone%20camera.%20Around%201%2C000%20people%20have%20joined%20him%20for%20the%20fast%20on%20March%2013%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20resentment%20among%20people%2C%20but%20we%20hope%20that%20this%20shows%20the%20central%20%5BUnion%5D%20government%20how%20serious%20the%20matter%20is%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20struggle%20will%20take%20long%2C%20but%20we%20are%20ready%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20also%20commented%20later%2C%20in%20reply%20to%20other%20questions%20posed%20by%20activists%20and%20members%20of%20the%20media%20during%20the%20virtual%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWangchuk%20also%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%E2%80%9Csurprised%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20government%20is%20not%20paying%20attention%20to%20their%20protest%20in%20such%20a%20sensitive%20region%2C%20which%20is%20surrounded%20by%20international%20borders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELadakhis%20have%20supported%20the%20Indian%20army%2C%20shoulder-to-shoulder%2C%20on%20every%20occasion%20across%20decades%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20%5Bthe%20government%5D%20will%20lose%20a%20great%20friend%20if%20they%20keep%20