er%20than%20usual%20and%20supplies%20villages%20in%20Ladakh%20with%20a%20constant%20water%20supply%20%E2%80%93%20has%20called%20on%20people%20across%20the%20country%20to%20join%20him%20on%20his%20climate%20fast%20for%20a%20single%20day%20%E2%80%93%20on%20Sunday%20(March%2017)%20%E2%80%93%20to%20show%20their%20solidarity%20and%20support%20for%20the%20movement.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20activists%20and%20environmentalists%20across%20the%20country%20are%20responding.%20People%20and%20organizations%20across%20several%20cities%20and%20towns%20in%20India%20have%20formed%20groups%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Wangchuk%E2%80%99s%20climate%20fast%2C%20and%20have%20pledged%20to%20fast%20on%20March%2017%20to%20show%20support%20for%20Ladakh%20and%20its%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFOLFON%20founder%20Dilip%20Jain%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20his%20organisation%20has%2020%20active%20chapters.%20These%20include%20activists%20and%20groups%20across%20several%20states%20including%20Uttarakhand%2C%20Rajasthan%2C%20Punjab%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3B%20and%20city%20chapters%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Kolhapur%2C%20Pune%20and%20Nagpur%20in%20Maharashtra%3B%20Coimbatore%20and%20Chennai%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%3B%20Bengaluru%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Hyderabad%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-1024x600.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-1024x600.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13232605%2FTso-Moriri-425