0called%20upon%20the%20people%20to%20stand%20strong%20together%20and%20ensure%20his%20party's%20victory%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Bsave%26quot%3B%20the%20Constitution%20and%20democracy%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20everyone%20should%20have%20equal%20opportunity%20in%20an%20election%2C%20Mr%20Kharge%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20freezing%20Congress'%20bank%20accounts%20and%20imposing%20huge%20fines%20on%20the%20party%20through%20Income%20Tax%2C%20while%20%26quot%3Bthey%20are%20not%20ready%20to%20disclose%20thousands%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20they%20have%20got%20through%20electoral%20bonds%2C%20despite%20Supreme%20Court's%20directions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20our%20party%20money%20that%20you%20the%20people%20gave%20as%20donations%2C%20they%20have%20frozen%20it%20and%20we%20don't%20have%20money%20to%20spend.....while%2C%20they%20(BJP)%20are%20not%20disclosing%20about%20electoral%20bonds%20they%20got%20because%20their%20theft%20will%20come%20out%2C%20their%20wrong%20deeds%20will%20come%20out%2C%20so%20they%20asked%20for%20time%20till%20July%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Kalaburagi%20(Gulbarga)%2C%20from%20where%20he%20unsuccessfully%20contested%20in%202019%20elections%2C%20have%20decided%20to%20%26quot%3Brectify%20their%20mistake%26quot%3B%20and%20make%20Congress%20victorious%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kharge%20was%20defeated%20by%20BJP's%20Umesh%20Jadhav%20in%20Gulbarga%20by%20a%20margin%20of%2095%2C452%20votes%20in%20the%20previous%20elections.%20Popularly%20known%20as%20%26quot%3BSolillada%20Saradara%26quot%3B%2C%20(a%20leader%20without%20defeat)%2C%20that%20was%20the%20first%20electoral%20loss%20in%20his%20political%20life%20spanning%20several%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeculation%20is%20rife%20that%20Mr%20Kharge%2C%20who%20has%20the%20role%20of%20managing%20the%20party%20natio