timesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Frussia-ready-to-use-nuclear-weapon-if-putin-warns-again%2Famp_articleshow%2F108471757.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gautam%20Adani%20Explains%20How%20Adani%20Group%20Countered%20Short-Seller's%20Attack%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAdani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Mumbai%20explained%20to%20the%20audience%20how%20the%20conglomerate%20countered%20false%20allegations%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20matter%2C%20came%20out%20stronger%2C%20and%20bounced%20back%20in%20no%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20my%20first%20reaction%20was%20concerned%20-%20when%20the%20news%20first%20came%2C%20I%20could%20see%20that%20the%20published%20material%20was%20all%20old%20allegations%2C%20which%20had%20been%20recycled%20in%20a%20different%20way.%20Such%20attacks%20were%20not%20new%20-%20and%20I%20felt%20that%2C%20like%20many%20earlier%20attacks%20on%20us%2C%20this%20too%20will%20pass%20quickly.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20business%20as%20usual%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%2C%20however%2C%20acknowledge%20it%20was%20a%20sophisticated%20form%20of%20attack%20on%20the%20conglomerate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Hindenburg%20attack%20on%20Adani%20was%20the%20world's%20biggest%20attack%20on%20a%20corporate.%20I%20also%20have%20no%20hesitation%20in%20saying%20that%20this%20attack%20was%20a%20unique%20two-dimensional%20attack%2C%20compared%20to%20typical%20short-seller%20attacks%20which%20are%20one-dimensional.%20This%20attack%20on%20us%20not%20only%20played%20out%20in%20the%20financial%20market%20but%20also%20played%20out%20in%20the%20political%20theatre.%20Both%20played%20out%20in%20conjunction%2C%20complementing%20and%20reinforcing%20each%20other%2C%20ably%20supported%20by%20a%20section%20of%20the%20media%2C%20both%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20Adani%20Group%20%26quot%3Binitially%20grossly%20underestimated%20the%20impact%20of%20this%20report%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20very%20soon%2C%20we%20understood%20the%20conspiracy%20and%20its%20depth.%20With%20no%20precedence%20to%20handle%20a%20crisis%20of%20this%20nature%20and%20magnitude%2C%20we%20evolved%20our%20own%20contra-strategy%20to%20handle%20it%20-%20and%20the%20rest%2C%20as%20they%20say%2C%20is%20history%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20steps%20the%20conglomerate%20took%20following%20the%20short-seller's%20attack%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20said%20the%20first%20step%20was%20to%20return%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20follow-on%20public%20offer%20(FPO)%20of%20Rs%2020%2C000%20crore%20on%20%26quot%3Bmoral%20grounds%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20then%20created%20a%20strong%20war-chest%20of%20cash%20of%20Rs%2070%2C000%20crore%2C%20prepaid%20Rs%2017%2C500%20crore%20of%20margin-linked%20financing%2C%20and%20insulated%20CEOs%20and%20executives%20from%20the%20noise.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20them%20to%20tighten%20their%20belt%20and%20focus%20on%20business%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20conglomerate%20further%20maintained%20the%20growth%20momentum%20and%20continued%20with%20expansion%20and%20new%20projects%20like%20Khavda%2C%20Dharavi%2C%20copper%20smelter%20-%20just%20to%20name%20a%20few.%20It%20created%20a%20war-room%20and%20answered%20all%20questions%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20said%2C%20adding%20they%20executed%20an%20extensive%20engagement%20programme%20with%20all%20their%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20key%20takeaways%2C%20according%20to%20Mr%20Adani%2C%20are%20cash%20is%20king%2C%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20engagement%20and%20strong%20communications%20with%20all%20stakeholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20biggest%20learning%20was%20that%20doing%20a%20good%20job%20is%20not%20enough%20-%20we%20must%20tell%20our%20story%20too.%20We%20need%20to%20communicate%20more%20-%20and%20communicate%20timely%20and%20more%20effectively%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20also%20like%20to%20conclude%20by%20sharing%20that%2C%20in%20this%20whole%20Hindenburg%20affair%2C%20what%20pained%20me%20the%20most%20was%20that%20many%20retail%20shareholders%20lost%20money.%20I%20feel%20extremely%20bad%20for%20them%20as%20they%20lost%20money%20for%20no%20reason.%20There%20never%20was%20any%20truth%20in%20all%20those%20allegations%20-%20and%20this%20was%20later%20validated%20when%20our%20companies%20regained%20their%20financial%20value%20in%20the%20capital%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Adani%20Group%20Chairman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710350460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2F477cnmoo_gautam-adani_625x300_13_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-explains-how-adani-group-countered-short-seller-hindenburg-attack-5233295%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Mumbai%20explained%20to%20the%20audience%20how%20the%20conglomerate%20countered%20false%20allegations%20in%20the%20Hindenburg%20matter%2C%20came%20out%20stronger%2C%20and%20bounced%20back%20in%20no%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-explains-how-adani-group-countered-short-seller-hindenburg-attack-5233295%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-explains-how-adani-group-countered-short-seller-hindenburg-attack-5233295%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-explains-how-adani-group-countered-short-seller-hinden