ted%20its%20first%20loss%20in%20over%20three%20decades%20Wednesday%20due%20to%20the%20fallout%20from%20the%20end%20of%20its%20collaboration%20with%20Kanye%20West%2C%20but%20the%20company%20insisted%20it%20was%20starting%20to%20turn%20its%20fortunes%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20late%202022%2C%20the%20German%20sportswear%20giant%20ended%20its%20contract%20with%20the%20US%20rapper%2C%20now%20known%20formally%20as%20Ye%2C%20after%20he%20triggered%20an%20outcry%20with%20a%20series%20of%20anti-Semitic%20social%20media%20posts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdidas%20and%20West%20had%20designed%20the%20blockbuster%20line%20of%20Yeezy%20trainers%20together%2C%20and%20the%20collapse%20of%20the%20partnership%20robbed%20the%20company%20of%20a%20vital%20revenue%20stream%2C%20and%20left%20it%20saddled%20with%20a%20massive%20stock%20of%20unsold%20footwear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdidas%20registered%20a%20loss%20of%2075%20million%20euros%20(%2482%20million)%20in%202023%20following%20a%20profit%20of%20612%20million%20euros%20the%20previous%20year.%20It%20was%20the%20company's%20first%20net%20loss%20since%201992%2C%20Adidas%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20CEO%20Bjorn%20Gulden%2C%20who%20was%20brought%20in%20to%20lead%20the%20company%20from%20rival%20outfitter%20Puma%20shortly%20after%20the%20West%20tie-up%20fell%20apart%2C%20struck%20an%20upbeat%20tone.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20turn%20the%20business%20(around)...%20The%20result%20is%20of%20course%20not%20good%20enough%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20it%20builds%20the%20base%20to%20actually%20achieve%20what%20we%20have%20promised.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202023%20results%20were%20not%20as%20bad%20as%20had%20been%20previously%20feared%2C%20and%20by%20%26quot%3B2025%20we%20should%20already%20be%20a%20good%20company%20and%20by%202026%20we%20should%20be%20a%20really%20healthy%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Transition%20year'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERevenues%20fell%20by%20five%20percent%20to%2021.4%20billion%20euros%2C%20and%20were%20hit%20particularly%20hard%20in%20the%20United%20States%20due%20to%20the%20discontinuation%20of%20sales%20of%20Yeezy%20trainers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdidas%20has%20been%20gradually%20seeking%20to%20offload%20the%20Yeezy%20trainers%2C%20with%20two%20sales%20in%202023%20bringing%20in%20750%20million%20euros.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20below%20the%201.2%20billion%20euros%20of%20revenue%20they%20had%20generated%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20expects%20to%20sell%20off%20the%20final%20Yeezy%20shoes%20this%20year%20at%20cost%2C%20resulting%20in%20revenues%20of%20around%20250%20million%20euros.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20sales%20fell%20heavily%20in%20North%20America%2C%20and%20are%20expected%20to%20keep%20declining%20this%20year%2C%20they%20picked%20up%20strongly%20in%20China%2C%20in%20good%20news%20from%20an%20important%20market%20which%20had%20suffered%20due%20to%20the%20country's%20tough%20coronavirus%20curbs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGulden%20has%20sought%20to%20focus%20on%20promoting%20classic%20Adidas%20trainers%20--such%20as%20Samba%2C%20Gazelle%20and%20Campus%20--%20and%20Adidas%20said%20sales%20of%20the%20products%20were%20growing%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdidas%20is%20forecasting%20a%20pick-up%20in%20business%20for%202024%2C%20with%20sales%20expected%20to%20grow%20in%20the%20%26quot%3Bmid%20single-digit%26quot%3B%20range%2C%20and%20operating%20profit%20to%20come%20in%20at%20around%20500%20million%20euros%2C%20double%20the%20figure%20for%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Germany%20to%20host%20the%20European%20football%20championships%20in%20June-July%2C%20and%20Paris%20the%20Olympics%20right%20after%2C%20Adidas%20is%20poised%20to%20bag%20additional%20sales%20from%20jerseys%20and%20related%20merchandise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20company's%20forecast%20was%20