0seeing%20her.%20It%20makes%20me%20so%20happy%20that%20she%20was%20able%20to%20see%20me%20play%20cricket%20for%20England.%20I'm%20proud%20that%20she%20could%20collect%20some%20of%20the%20awards%20I%20have%20won%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20when%20I%20couldn't%20be%20there%20and%20I%20know%20she%20enjoyed%20doing%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20England%20batter%20revealed%20that%20he%20decided%20to%20leave%20the%20India%20Test%20tour%20after%20he%20was%20informed%20his%20%26quot%3Bgrandmother%20was%20ill%20and%20didn't%20have%20long%20left.%26quot%3B%20After%20his%20grandmother%20passed%20away%2C%20the%2025-year-old%20batter%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20be%20around%20his%20family%20while%20they%20are%20grieving.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20made%20the%20decision%20to%20leave%20the%20India%20test%20tour%20the%20night%20before%20we%20flew%20from%20Abu%20Dhabi%20to%20India%20because%20I%20was%20told%20for%20the%20first%20time%20that%20my%20Grandmother%20was%20ill%20and%20didn't%20have%20long%20left.%20Now%20that%20she%20has%20passed%20my%20family%20%26amp%3B%20I%20are%20grieving%20and%20I%20need%20to%20be%20around%20them.%20Over%20the%20last%20few%20years%20I%20have%20learned%20to%20prioritise%20my%20mental%20well-being%20and%20that%20of%20my%20family's%2C%20honestly%20nothing%20is%20more%20important%20to%20me%20than%20family.%20So%20whilst%20this%20may%20come%20as%20surprising%20to%20some%2C%20I%20know%20it's%20the%20right%20decision%20for%20me.%20I'm%20young%20and%20hope%20to%20have%20many%2C%20many%20more%20years%20of%20cricket%20to%20come%20which%20I%20intend%20to%20make%20the%20absolute%20most%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExpressing%20gratefulness%20for%20the%20support%20he%20received%20from%20the%20England%20and%20Wales%20Cricket%20Board%20(ECB)%20and%20his%20IPL%20franchise%20Delhi%20Capitals%2C%20Brook%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20couldn't%20be%20more%20grateful%20for%20the%20support%20I%20have%20received%2C%20esp