business%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20and%20the%20city%20taught%20him%20to%20think%20big%2C%20dream%20big%20and%20above%20all%2C%20aspire%20to%20succeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThereafter%2C%20just%20as%20I%20was%20about%20to%20turn%2019%20and%20was%20settling%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20life%20took%20an%20unexpected%20turn.%20I%20was%20called%20back%20by%20my%20elder%20brother%20to%20assist%20in%20running%20a%20small-scale%20PVC%20film%20factory%20we%20had%20acquired%20near%20Ahmedabad.%20The%20business%20was%20challenging%20due%20to%20the%20scarcity%20of%20raw%20materials%20caused%20by%20heavy%20import%20restrictions%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20all%20this%20was%20set%20to%20change%20following%20the%20elections%20in%201985.%20Rajiv%20Gandhi%20had%20just%20become%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20he%20initiated%20the%20liberalisation%20of%20import%20policies.%20Despite%20having%20no%20experience%2C%20I%20grabbed%20the%20opportunity%20and%20swiftly%20established%20a%20trading%20organisation%20and%20began%20importing%20polymers%20to%20supply%20to%20the%20needy%20small-scale%20industries...%20This%20start%20of%20liberalisation%20gave%20me%20my%20first%20big%20break.%20I%20was%2023%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20Mr%20Adani%20said%2C%20the%20%26quot%3Bjourney%20is%20only%20just%20starting%2C%20a%20journey%20built%20on%20one%20of%20the%20most%20exciting%20platforms%20that%20has%20ever%20existed%20-%20a%20platform%20called%20India.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20last%20three%20decades%20since%20the%201990s%20have%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20India%20to%20become%20the%20world's%20fifth-largest%20economy%2C%20the%20journey%20towards%202050%20will%20be%20even%20more%20transformative%20and%20disruptive.%20While%20the%20past%20three%20decades%20were%20about%20opening%20India%20to%20the%20world%2C%20the%20upcoming%20three%20decades%20will%20see%20the%20world%20opening%20up%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Adani%20Group%20Chairman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20digital%20age%20has%20democratised%20the%20playing%20field.%20It%20has%20thrown%20open%20opportunities%20to%20a%20far%20greater%20number%20of%20companies.%20This%20is%20the%20age%20of%20exponential%20growth.%20And%20the%20most%20striking%20manifestation%20of%20this%20digital%20revolution%20is%20the%20emergence%20of%20new%20disruptive%20tech%20billionaires.%20An%20interesting%20statistic%20is%20that%20in%20the%201990s%2C%20India%20had%20just%20two%20billionaires.%20Today%2C%20the%20number%20is%20167%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20started%20my%20entrepreneurship%20journey%20in%20my%20teens.%20Entrepreneurship%20is%20about%20taking%20risks%20and%20being%20OK%20with%20sometimes%20getting%20lost%2C%20sometimes%20falling%20-%20but%20every%20time%20I%20was%20lost%2C%20every%20time%20I%20fell%20-%20I%20was%20still%20able%20to%20find%20my%20way%20back.%20I%20was%20still%20able%20to%20get%20up.%20I%20never%20feared%20falling%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%20explained%20five%20principles%20that%20have%20guided%20him%20in%20entrepreneurship%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20all%20success%20will%20come%20with%20its%20challenges%20and%20its%20challengers.%20%26quot%3BThe%20greater%20your%20success%2C%20bigger%20will%20you%20be%20as%20a%20target%20and%20the%20true%20measure%20of%20your%20success%20will%20not%20be%20in%20your%20achievements%20but%20in%20your%20ability%20to%20rise%20through%20the%20adversities%20that%20will%20come%20with%20your%20achievements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20the%20world%20is%20complex%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20be%20sold%20on%20the%20theory%20of%20simplicity.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20simplicity%20may%20be%20the%20goal%2C%20it%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20manage%20complexity%20that%20will%20differentiate%20you%20and%20make%20you%20the%20ones%20that%20can%20navigate%20the%20deep%20waters%20as%20against%20those%20that%20remain%20on%20the%20shallow%20shores.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20the%20dynamic%20model%20of%20a%20fast-growing%20nation%20like%20India%20needs%20a%20flexible%20approach%20that%20is%20rooted%20in%20local%20models%20as%20against%20models%20that%20often%20emphasise%20specialisation%20and%20core%20competencies.%20%26quot%3BThe%20crux%20of%20strategic%20differentiation%20often%20lies%20in%20recognising%20the%20limitations%20of%20bookish%20knowledge%20and%20Western%20centric%20models.%20While%20it%20is%20important%20to%20source%20ideas%20from%20books%20and%20literature%2C%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20these%20are%20after%20all%20opinions%20of%20brilliant%20story%20tellers%20with%20great%20ability%20to%20influence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFourth%2C%20resilience%20often%20requires%20the%20ability%20to%20withstand%20criticism.%20%26quot%3BThe%20higher%20you%20rise%2C%20the%20more%20you%20will%20need%20to%20prepare%20yourself%20to%20handle%20criticism.%20But%20instead%20of%20allowing%20it%20to%20deter%20progress%2C%20you%20must%20be%20willing%20to%20be%20misunderstood%2C%20and%20yet%20stay%20resilient.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20is%20about%20cultivating%20an%20inner%20strength%20that%20allows%20you%20to%20remain%20strong%20in%20your%20convictions%2C%20even%20in%20the%20face%20of%20severe%20opposition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20fifth%2C%20the%20most%20difficult%20of%20all%20-%20stay%20humble.%20%26quot%3BYour%20own%20success%20will%20push%20back%20on%20your%20humility.%20But%20humility%20is%20the%20biggest%20differentiator%20you%20can%20build.%20Humility%20is%20not%20thinking%20less%20of%20yourself%20-%20it%20is%20thinking%20of%20yourself%20a%20little%20less.%20True%20leadership%20lies%20in%20acknowledging%20your%20achievements%20without%20letting%20them%20overshadow%20the%20value%20of%20self-awareness.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Adani%20said%20the%20two%20people%20who%20deeply%20influenced%20him%20during%20his%20formative%20years%20were%20his%20parents.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20mother%20was%20the%20pillar%20of%20our%20household%20and%20instrumental%20in%20keeping%20our%20joint%20family%20tightly-knit.%20Her%20commitment%20to%20hold%20our%20large%20family%20together%20laid%20the%20foundation%20of%20my%20family%20values%20and%20beliefs.%20And%20the%20second%20was%20my%20father%20who%20was%20in%20the%20business%20of%20forward%20trading.%20In%20those%20days%2C%20the%20transactions%20happened%20verbally%2C%20mostly%20on%20the%20telephone%2C%20without%20any%20written%20documents%2C%20or%20contracts.%20At%20a%20very%20young%20age%20I%20saw%20that%20these%20verbal%20commitments%20never%20failed%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Adani%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20experiences%20from%20my%20childhood%20played%20a%20significant%20part%20in%20shaping%20my%20beliefs%2C%20and%20resulted%20in%20what%20today%20are%20the%20core%20values%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20-%20the%20courage%20to%20withstand%2C%20the%20trust%20in%20people%2C%20and%20the%20commitment%20to%20a%20larger%20cause%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710348360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fafr1tnho_gautam-adani_625x300_16_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-on-5-principles-of-success-and-challenges-he-faced-5233088%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Adani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Mumbai%20recalled%20his%20long%20journey%20as%20an%20entrepreneur%20and%20shared%20lessons%20learned%20from%20challenges%20that%20he%20faced%20along%20the%20way.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgautam-adani-on-5-principles-of