1%2C000%20aspirants%20were%20contacted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20policeman%20and%20assembled%20-%20some%20were%20moved%20in%20buses%20-%20at%20a%20resort%20in%20Haryana%2C%20where%20they%20were%20given%20the%20answer%20key%20and%20the%20question%20paper%20for%20the%20UP%20Police%20Constable%20exam%20held%20on%20February%2017%20and%2018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhones%20and%20gadgets%20were%20seized%2C%20and%20they%20were%20made%20to%20commit%20answers%20to%20memory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20has%20seen%20visuals%20from%20the%20'cram%20session'%20-%20held%20two%20days%20before%20the%20exam%20-%20which%20shows%20dozens%20of%20young%20men%20and%20women%20sitting%20in%20rows%20on%20a%20lawn%20and%20reading%20from%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20each%20person%20paid%20Rs%207%20lakh%20-%20to%20be%20paid%20after%20the%20exam%20-%20for%20leaked%20papers.%20The%20accused%20would%20retain%20original%20marksheets%20from%20previous%20exams%20as%20%26quot%3Binsurance%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20exam%20papers%20and%20answer%20keys%20were%20procured%20from%20two%20other%20people%2C%20identified%20simply%20as%20Abhishek%20Shukla%2C%20from%20UP's%20Prayagraj%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Attri%2C%20who%20is%20a%20resident%20of%20UP's%20Greater%20Noida%20and%20was%20involved%20in%20the%202015%20AIPMT%2C%20or%20All%20India%20Pre-Medical%20and%20Pre-Dental%20Test%2C%20paper%20leak%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20believe%20Attri%20and%20Shukla%20could%20be%20the%20final%20pieces%20in%20this%20jigsaw%20puzzle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20arrest%20and%20interrogation%20of%20Ravi%20and%20Abhishek%20could%20be%20the%20last%20link%20in%20this%20investigation%20and%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Additional%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Brijesh%20Kumar%20Singh%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday's%20arrest%20comes%20a%20month%20after%2015%20others%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20for%20allegedly%20planning%20to%20leak%20question%20papers%20for%20the%20same%20exam.%20In%20that%20instance%20the%20accused%20were%20taking%20payments%20upto%20Rs%208%20lakh%20per%20aspirant.%20That%20edition%20of%20the%20exam%20was%20cancelled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-cancels-police-constable-recruitment-exam-after-paper-leak-allegations-5118905%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUP%20Cancels%20Police%20Constable%20Recruitment%20Exam%2C%20Orders%20Re-Test%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%2048%20lakh%20men%20and%20women%20sat%20for%20that%20exam%2C%20which%20was%20cancelled%20days%20later%20amid%20multiple%20paper%20leak%20reports.%20UP%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20said%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20can%20be%20no%20compromise%20with%20the%20sanctity%20of%20examinations.%20Those%20who%20toy%20with%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20youngsters%20will%20not%20be%20spared%20under%20any%20circumstances.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnational-sin-yogi-adityanath-vows-strict-against-up-exam-paper-leak-5124559%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BNational%20Sin%26quot%3B%3A%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20Vows%20Strict%20In%20UP%20Exam%20Paper%20Leak%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%20last%20month%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20passed%20an%20'anti-cheating'%20bill%20to%20check%20fraudulent%20practices%20such%20as%20these%20-%20the%20leaking%20of%20exam%20papers%20for%20government%20recruitment%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flok-sabha-passes-bill-to-prevent-paper-leaks-cheating-5005606%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELok%20Sabha%20Passes%20Key%20Bill%20To%20Prevent%20Paper%20Leaks%2C%20Cheating%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20this%20bill%2C%20students%20who%20take%20competitive%20exams%20in%20good%20faith%20(i.e.%2C%20they%20do%20not%20knowingly%20seek%20to%20profit%20from%20cheating)%20will%20not%20be%20targeted.%20However%2C%20those%20who%20leak%20exam%20papers%20or%20tamper%20with%20answer%20sheets%2C%20by%20colluding%20with%20officials%20will%20face%20up%20to%2010%20years%20in%20jail%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%201%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710343620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fssa3rp1_up-exam-paper-leak-case_625x300_13_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-police-constable-exam-paper-leak-case-rs-7-lakh-fee-haryana-resort-up-police-crack-exam-paper-leak-case-5232168%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20associate%20of%20a%20Delhi%20Police%20constable%20was%20arrested%20by%20a%20special%20task%20force%20of%20his%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20colleagues%20Wednesday%20evening%2C%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20exam%20paper%20leak%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-police-constable-exam-paper-leak-case-rs-7-lakh-fee-haryana-resort-up-police-crack-exam-paper-leak-case-5232168%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-police-constable-exam-paper-leak-case-rs-7-lakh-fee-haryana-resort-up-police-crack-exam-paper-leak-case-5232168%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fup-police-constable-exam-paper-leak-case-rs-7-lakh-fee-haryana-resort-up-police-crack-exam-paper-leak-case-5232168%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20passes%20bill%20that%20would%