%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1433-joe-root-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJoe%20Root%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20the%204-1%20win%20in%20the%20recently-concluded%20five-match%20series.%20Ashwin%20mentioned%20Anderson's%20claims%20ahead%20of%20Day%204%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20match%20where%20he%20said%20that%20England%20will%20look%20to%20chase%20down%20the%20399-run%20target%20within%2060%20overs.%20The%20result%20is%20quite%20different%20as%20the%20visitors%20were%20bowled%20out%20and%20defeated%20comprehensively.%20Ashwin%20expressed%20surprise%20at%20the%20over%20the%20top%20statement%20and%20said%20that%20although%20it%20was%20a%20show%20of%20positive%20mindset%2C%20the%20statement%20%26quot%3Bwent%20too%20far%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJames%20Anderson%20went%20into%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20after%20winning%20the%20first%20considerably%20well.%20Much%20respect%20to%20them%20for%20winning%20that.%20He%20told%20the%20press%20that%20even%20if%20the%204th%20innings%20target%20was%20500%20or%20600%2C%20we'll%20finish%20it%20in%2060%20overs.%20Even%20though%20it%20was%20an%20example%20of%20their%20positive%20mindset%2C%20it%20felt%20like%20they%20had%20gone%20too%20far%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ashwin%20said%20on%20his%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZU2H3gZx7tE%5C%22%3E%20YouTube%20channel%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20also%20believes%20that%20Bazball%20leans%20more%20towards%20being%20a%20'defenseless%20cricket'%20and%20although%20Joe%20Root%20is%20a%20great%20player%20of%20spin%2C%20his%20game%20was%20also%20impacted%20due%20to%20the%20style%20of%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20one%20thing%20I%20understood%20after%20the%20first%20Test%20is%20that%20Bazball%20isn't%20just%20aggressive%20cricket.%20It%20is%20defenseless%20cricket.%20They%20aren't%20going%20to%20play%20a%20defensive%20shot%20at%20all.%20They%20are%20going%20to%20get%20out%20if%20they%20play%20defense.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20Joe%20Root%20also%20agreed%20to%20their%20game%20plan.%20Because%20if%20you%20take%20world%20cricket's%20vest%20defense%20rankings%2C%20Root%20is%20an%20easy%20number%201%20on%20that%20list%20against%20spin.%20He%20also%20bought%20into%20their%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20second%20day%20of%20the%20Rajkot%20Test%20match%2C%20Ashwin%20dismissed%20England's%20Zak%20Crawley%20to%20pocket%20his%20500th%20Test%20scalp.%20Before%20him%2C%20only%20Anil%20Kumble%20reached%20the%20milestone%20among%20Indians.%20He%20became%20the%20ninth%20bowler%20worldwide%20to%20take%20500%20wickets.%20However%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20feat%2C%20Ashwin%20went%20through%20a%20traumatic%20experience%20for%20which%20he%20had%20to%20leave%20the%20squad%20on%20an%20immediate%20basis.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BRavichandran%20Ashwin%20has%20withdrawn%20from%20the%20Test%20squad%2C%20effective%20immediately%20due%20to%20a%20family%20medical%20emergency.%20In%20these%20challenging%20times%2C%20the%20Board%20of%20Control%20for%20Cricket%20in%20India%20(BCCI)%20and%20the%20team%20fully%20supports%20Ashwin%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20BCCI%20in%20its%20release.%20Reports%20said%20Ashwin's%20mother%20Chitra%20had%20suffered%20a%20medical%20emergency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Ashwin%20has%20revealed%20how%20exactly%20thing%20transpired.%20%26quot%3BWe%20went%20to%20the%20dressing%20room%20for%20another%20debrief%20and%20then%20back%20to%20our%20rooms.%20Rohit%2C%20me%2C%20and%20others%20were%20just%20discussing%20some%20things%20about%20the%20match%20here%20and%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20when%20I%20realized%20I%20was%20not%20getting%20calls%20from%20my%20parents%20or%20wife.%20I%20thought%20they%20were%20busy%20attending%20calls%20and%20giving%20interviews.%20I%20called%20my%20wife%20around%207%20PM%2C%20asking%20why%20my%20parents%20weren't%20answering%20my%20call.%20Her%20voice%20was%20a%20bit%20shaky.%20She%20asked%20me%20to%20come%20separately%20from%20the%20crowd%20and%20told%20me%20that%20my%20mother%20collapsed%20after%20a%20headache%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20blanked%20out.%20I%20did%20not%20know%20how%20to%20react%20or%20what%20questions%20to%20ask.%20I%20was%20crying%20but%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20nobody%20was%20watching%20me%20cry.%20It%20is%20unnecessary%20to%20think%20of%20it%20that%20way%2C%20but%20it%20was%20instinctive.%20I%20could%20not%20think.%20I%20was%20crying%20in%20my%20room%20for%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%2C%20the%20team%20physio%20checked%20on%20me%20as%20I%20was%20not%20picking%20up%20calls.%20Rahul%20Bhai%20and%20Rohit%20Bhai%20also%20came%20to%20check%20on%20me%2C%20and%20all%20I%20could%20tell%20them%20was%20that%20I%20could%20not%20think%20clearly%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710342600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fv5gq4ueg_sf_625x300_12_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fgone-too-far-ravichandran-ashwin-names-james-anderson-joe-root-in-damning-review-of-bazball-5225426%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20gave%20a%20damning%20verdict%20on%20Bazball%20with%20special%20mentions%20for%20James%20Anderson%20and%20Joe%20Root%20following%20the%204-1%20win%20in%20the%20recently-concluded%20five-match%20series.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'In%20Haiti%2C%20we're%20living%20with%20death%20on%20a%20daily%20basis'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710342086000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FF906%2Fproduction%2F_132905736_annie-creditannie.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-latin-america-68555689%234%22%2C%22s