hief%20minister%20in%20Khattar%20government%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20entire%20political%20drama%20was%20to%20unseat%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHolding%20show%20of%20strength%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Hisar%2C%20Chautala%20said%20the%20BJP%20was%20getting%20wary%20in%20the%20alliance%20because%20JJP%20was%20seen%20as%20more%20active%20in%20the%20Khattar%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBJP%20MLAs%20often%20confided%20in%20me%20that%20raj%20tau%20aap%20hi%20chala%20rahe%20(you%20are%20the%20one%20running%20the%20government)%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Chautala%20whose%20party%20had%20just%2010%20MLAs%20against%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2040%20in%20the%20alliance%20that%20was%20not%20originally%20planned%20during%202019%20assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20parties%20fought%20the%20last%20assembly%20election%20against%20each%20other%20and%20only%20came%20together%20in%20the%20post-election%20scenario%20after%20BJP%20fell%20short%20of%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20alliance%20had%20a%20smooth%20run%20in%20the%20last%20four%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20restlessness%20was%20growing%20among%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20possibly%20because%20Dushyant%20was%20hogging%20more%20limelight%2C%20something%20he%20also%20mentioned%20in%20his%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20curtains%20finally%20closed%20on%20the%20alliance%2C%20Dushyant%2C%20as%20expected%2C%20owned%20several%20achievements%20of%20Khattar%20government%20as%20his%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20whether%2050%25%20reservation%20of%20women%20in%20local%20bodies%2C%20or%2075%25%20reservations%20for%20Haryana%20youth%20in%20private%20jobs%2C%20all%20these%20welfare%20schemes%20became%20possible%20in%20the%20Khattar%20government%20because%20of%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20active%20involvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDushyant%20said%20it%20was%20because%20of%20the%20JJP%20that%20interest%20of%20farmers%2C%20labourers%20and%20Dalits%20got%20prominence%20and%20were%20given%20benefit%20of%20government%20schemes.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CI%20am%20hopeful%20that%20the%20new%20government%20under%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20will%20continue%20welfare%20schemes%20started%20in%20the%20previous%20government%20because%20of%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDusyant%E2%80%99s%20father%20and%20JJP%E2%80%99s%20national%20president%20Ajay%20Chautala%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20also%20hinted%20that%20seat%20sharing%20dispute%20was%20cited%20as%20an%20excuse%20to%20end%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20demanded%20two%20seats%20from%20the%20BJP%20but%20they%20denied%20and%20later%20snapped%20the%20ties%20with%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20while%20hitting%20out%20at%20the%20saffron%20party%20saying%20that%20the%20latter%20did%20not%20follow%20alliance%20dharma.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CWe%20supported%20BJP%20on%20all%20occasions%20but%20they%20did%20not.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20next%20course%20of%20action%2C%20both%20the%20father-son%20duo%20said%20they%20would%20definitely%20fight%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20and%20they%20would%20decide%20in%20coming%20days%20on%20the%20number%20of%20seats%20that%20they%20would%20contest.%C2%A0They%20said%20their%20final%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20majority%20on%20their%20own%20in%20the%20assembly%20polls%20later%20this%20year%20and%20for%20this%2C%20the%20party%20workers%20were%20fully%20poised.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fharyana-cm-manohar-lal-khattar-resigns-amid-rift-between-bjp-jjp-alliance-over-seat-sharing%5C%22%3EHaryana%3A%20BJP%20Picks%20State%20Chief%20Nayab%20Singh%20Saini%20as%20New%20CM%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJJP%20came%20into%20existence%20only%20in%202018%2C%20after%20Ajay%20had%20a%20fall%20out%20with%20his%20brother%20Abhay%20Chautala%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Lok%20Dal%20(INLD)%2C%20whose%20founder%20was%20popular%20Jat%20leader%20of%20Haryana%20Chaudhary%20Devi%20Lal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESaini%20won%20floor%20test%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20taking%20the%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20Saini%20won%20the%20floor%20test%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20due%20to%20support%20of%20six%20independent%20MLAs.%20The%20Haryana%20assembly%20was%20convened%20on%20the%20request%20of%20Saini%20who%20wanted%20to%20prove%20his%20majority%20in%20the%20floor%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20trust%20vote%2C%20five%20out%20of%20the%2010%20JJP%20MLAs%20were%20present%20in%20the%20assembly.%20But%20after%20the%20JJP%20issued%20whip%20asking%20their%20MLAs%20to%20not%20attend%20the%20session%2C%20they%20went%20out%20and%20did%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20floor%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJJP%20state%20president%20Nishan%20Singh%20told%20media%20that%20all%20party%20MLAs%20are%20united%20even%20as%20divide%20in%20the%20party%20was%20clearly%20visible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20rally%2C%20Dushyant%20said%20that%20JJP%20was%20least%20worried%20of%20defection%20in%20the%20party.%20He%20mentioned%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20the%2070s%2C%20the%20then%20Congress%20leader%20Bhajan%20Lal%20took%20away%20most%20of%20our%20MLAs%20but%20did%20it%20finish%20us%3F%20Our%20real%20strength%20is%20our%20supporters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Saini%20said%20in%20his%20assembly%20address%20that%20people%20of%20the%20state%20have%20full%20confidence%20in%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20innumerable%20works%20that%20have%20been%20done%20by%20our%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Saini%20in%20the%20assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20contrary%2C%20Congress%20MLAs%20flayed%20the%20BJP%2C%20saying%20that%20change%20in%20the%20government%20showed%20that%20the%20party%20was%20a%20failure%20on%20all%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710341425000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13200940%2FScreen-Shot-2024-03-13-at-8.09.12-PM.png%22%2C%