ivisions%20(constituencies)%20which%20reported%20an%20abnormal%20decadal%20growth%20rate%20were%20Naga-dominated%20divisions%20of%20Mao-Maram%20(143.12%25)%2C%20Paomata%20(122.64%25)%20and%20Purul%20(168.78%25)%20sub-divisions%2C%20not%20of%20the%20Kukis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAtrocities%20against%20a%20particular%20community%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EN.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20in%20the%20House%20pointing%20the%20decadal%20growth%20of%20voters%20in%20Kuki-dominated%20constituencies%20to%2051%25%20from%20the%20previous%20decade%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20deep%20regret.%20This%20in%20fact%20is%20misleading%20that%20warrants%20attention%20from%20responsible%20authorities.%20Information%20from%20the%20office%20of%20the%20state%20election%20commission%20shows%20a%20decadal%20growth%20in%20Kuki%20areas%20at%2010.2%25%2C%20which%20is%20far%20below%20the%20population%20growth%20in%20Naga%20and%20Meitei%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20the%20attitude%20of%20the%20current%20Manipur%20government%2C%20as%20evident%20in%20the%20last%20assembly%20sitting%2C%20exemplifies%20the%20state%20of%20anarchy%20in%20a%20majoritarian%20democracy.%20Every%20session%20of%20the%20House%20exhibits%20the%20character%20of%20the%20far-right%20majoritarian%20democracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20constant%20vilification%20of%20Kukis%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20and%20in%20the%20House%20reminds%20us%20of%20the%20tactics%20of%20Joseph%20Goebbels%2C%20the%20propaganda%20minister%20of%20Adolf%20Hilter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoebbels%E2%80%99%20famous%20lines%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%20tell%20a%20lie%20big%20enough%20and%20keep%20repeating%20it%2C%20people%20will%20eventually%20come%20to%20believe%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20seems%20to%20be%20well%20applied%20today%20to%20the%20ignorant%20masses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20which%20initially%20stemmed%20from%20debates%20over%20the%20Meitei%E2%80%99s%20Schedule%20Tribe%20status%20has%20now%20evolved%20into%20a%20complex%20immigrant-refugee%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20framing%20the%20violence%20as%20a%20consequence%20of%20the%20refugee%20crisis%20fuelled%20by%20drug%20cartels%2C%20the%20state%20government%20not%20only%20captures%20the%20attention%20of%20central%20leaders%20but%20also%20rationalises%20its%20actions%20toward%20its%20own%20citizens%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20mobilises%20the%20entire%20Meitei%20population%2C%20as%20well%20as%20militant%20organisations%20like%20the%20UNLF(P)%20and%20right-wing%20associations%20such%20as%20Arambai%20Tenggol%20and%20Meitei%20Leepun%2C%20in%20the%20campaign%20against%20%E2%80%98illegal%20immigrants%2C%E2%80%99%20a%20term%20often%20loosely%20applied%20by%20the%20Meiteis%20to%20refer%20to%20the%20Kuki%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20doubt%20that%20illegal%20movements%20from%20neighbouring%20countries%20have%20taken%20place%20with%20loosely%20implemented%20border%20policies.%20And%20it%20is%20not%20a%20case%20of%20the%20Indo-Burma%20frontier%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20claim%20of%20a%20massive%20increase%20in%20the%20population%20of%20Kukis%20is%20not%20reflected%20in%20any%20of%20the%20official%20records%20in%20the%20past%20four%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%E2%80%99s%20latest%20data%20of%20above-normal%20growth%20in%20the%20voter%20list%20of%20Kukis%2C%20as%20presented%20in%20the%20House%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20means%20to%20garner%20mass%20support%20and%20continue%20further%20state-sponsored%20aggression%20towards%20its%20own%20citizens%20who%20voted%20him%20to%20power.%3Ca%20name%3D%5C%22_edn1%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-manipurs-assembly-session-reflects-the-states-struggle-with-crisis-management%23_ednref1%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20author%20is%20interested%20in%20northeast%20history%2C%20ethnic-relations%20and%20conflict%20resolutions.%20He%20can%20be%20reached%20at%20lienchongloi%40gmail.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710339451000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F11194911%2FF0ubs4CWcAEONzp.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-manipurs-assembly-session-reflects-the-states-struggle-with-crisis-management%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20was%20the%20second%20sitting%20of%20the%20House%20since%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20in%20May%20last%20year.%20But%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20discussion%20in%20the%20House%20highlights%20how%20helpless%20and%20vulnerable%20democracy%20has%20become%20for%20the%20minority%20communities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-manipurs-assembly-session-reflects-the-states-struggle-with-crisis-management%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20Spent%2015%20Years%20to%20Save%20One%20of%20Jharkhand%E2%80%99s%20Most%20Sustainable%20Artforms%20from%20the%20Impact%20of%20Migration%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20published%20in%20partnership%20with%20Samvaad%20%E2%80%93%20Enabled%20by%20Tata%20Steel%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%2015%20November%2C%202023%2C%20Sumanti%20Devi%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20red%20and%20white%20cotton%20saree%2C%20maintained%20a%20composed%20demeanour%20despite%20her%20excitement.%20With%20a%20job%20to%20fulfil%20and%20a%20role%20to%20embody%2C%20she%20concealed%20her%20feelings%20and%20prepared%20for%20the%20upcoming%20buzz%20at%20Jamshedpur%E2%80%99s%20Gopal%20Maidan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20my%20tenth%20year%20of%20putting%20up%20a%20stall%20at%20Samvaad%2C%20and%20yet