EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhome-ministrys-positive-narrative-on-caa-is-full-of-lies-half-truths-and-really-bad-drafting%5C%22%3EHome%20Ministry%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Positive%20Narrative%E2%80%99%20on%20CAA%20is%20Full%20of%20Lies%2C%20Half-Truths%20and%20Really%20Bad%20Drafting%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20underlined%20inconsistencies%20in%20the%20treatment%20of%20persecuted%20religious%20minorities%20from%20various%20countries%2C%20specifically%20highlighting%20the%20exclusion%20of%20persecuted%20groups%20such%20as%20the%20Sri%20Lankan%20Eelam%20Tamils.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20further%20emphasised%20the%20violation%20of%20the%20Assam%20Accord%20of%201985%2C%20which%20required%20the%20expulsion%20of%20foreigners%20who%20came%20to%20Assam%20after%20March%2025%2C%201971%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Sentinel%20%3C%2Fem%3Esaid%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20opposition%20leader%20%E2%80%9Cargued%20that%20providing%20citizenship%20to%20illegal%20who%20are%20non-Muslims%20contradicts%20the%20Accord%20and%20weakens%20the%20socio-economic%20fabric%20of%20the%20state.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20another%20petition%20at%20the%20SC%2C%20the%20All%20Assam%20Students%20Union%20(AASU)%20which%20had%20spearheaded%20the%20anti-foreigner%20agitation%20in%20Assam%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Flegitimizing-illegal-migration-all-assam-students-union-moves-supreme-court-challenging-citizenship-amendment-rules-2024-252044%5C%22%3Estated%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20court%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cthe%20notification%20of%20the%20Rules%20on%2011.3.2024%20stands%20in%20stark%20contradiction%20to%20the%20Assam%20Accord%20and%20Section%206A%20of%20the%20Citizenship%20Act%201955.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CAASU%20argues%20that%20these%20rules%20legitimise%20illegal%20migrants%2C%20adversely%20impacting%20indigenous%20culture%20and%20violating%20constitutional%20provisions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%20is%20yet%20to%20set%20a%20date%20to%20hear%20this%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20seeking%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20notification%20of%20the%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EProtest%20march%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20AASU%20organised%20a%20torchlight%20rally%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Guwahati%20on%20March%2012%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13180004%2FGIi040TXkAAyOFU.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13180004%2FGIi040TXkAAyOFU.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13180004%2FGIi040TXkAAyOFU-300x167.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13180004%2FGIi040TXkAAyOFU-1024x570.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-701494%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22668%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EProtest%20march%20organised%20by%20AASU.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40SamujjalBhatta%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELocal%20news%20reports%20said%20that%20protesters%20burnt%20effigies%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20at%20several%20locations.%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20reminder%20of%20the%202019%20protests%20against%20the%20Citizenship%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%20demonstrators%20have%20once%20again%20chanted%20slogans%20like%20%E