%2Fstrong%3E%20In%20an%20unusual%20move%2C%20the%20Union%20cabinet%20last%20week%20approved%20the%20Readjustment%20of%20Representation%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20Bill%2C%202024.%20It%20empowered%20the%20census%20commissioner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fgoa%2Fgoa-cm-sawant-thanks-modi-shah-for-cabinet-approval-of-bill-to-reserve-st-seats-in-state-assembly-2927819%5C%22%3Eto%20notify%20the%20population%20of%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20(STs)%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Goa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20observers%20in%20the%20state%20saw%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20March%207%20directive%20as%20a%20move%20to%20mollify%20the%20STs%20of%20Goa%20who%20have%20been%20demanding%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20the%20community%20in%20the%20assembly.%20The%20hurry%20in%20which%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20passed%20the%20directive%2C%20at%20the%20fag%20end%20of%20its%20tenure%2C%20can%20be%20appreciated%20better%20if%20one%20recalls%20Goa%20chief%20minister%20Pramod%20Sawant%E2%80%99s%20statement%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20last%20month.%20Sawant%20had%20told%20the%20House%20then%20that%20the%20reservation%20of%20assembly%20constituencies%20for%20STs%20would%20not%20be%20possible%20before%20the%20delimitation%20process%20expected%20countrywide%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20just%20days%20to%20go%20before%20the%20general%20elections%20are%20announced%2C%20the%20Centre%20made%20a%20sudden%20move%20on%20Goa.%20This%20matches%20the%20Bhartiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20government%E2%80%99s%20other%20recent%20express%20moves%20where%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20immediate%20political%20motive%20discernible%2C%20keeping%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20poll%20prospects%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20top%20leadership%20is%20focused%20on%20micro-managing%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20one%20at%20a%20time.%20This%20approach%20of%20the%20party%20to%20utilise%20the%20Central%20government%E2%80%99s%20powers%20to%20add%20leverage%20to%20its%202024%20prospects%2C%20in%20turn%20puts%20a%20question%20mark%20on%20the%20so-called%20invincibility%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Modi%20factor%E2%80%99%20on%20voters.%20Also%2C%20it%20calls%20to%20question%20how%20confident%20the%20party%20is%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20issue%2C%20beyond%20the%20Hindi%20belt.%20At%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%2C%20Modi%20pushed%20his%20way%20to%20play%20priest-king%2C%20casting%20all%20religious%20and%20secular%20convention%20aside.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Goa%20directive%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20minister%20Sawant%E2%80%99s%20February%2011%20statement%20in%20the%20Goa%20assembly%2C%20mentioned%20above%2C%20was%20in%20response%20to%20a%20calling-attention%20motion%20moved%20by%20the%20entire%20seven-member%20Opposition%20belonging%20to%20the%20Congress%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20Revolutionary%20Goan%20Party%20and%20Goa%20Forward%20Party.%20For%20over%20a%20year%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20strident%20protest%20in%20Goa%20around%20this%20demand.%20Opposition%20parties%20have%20also%20joined%20the%20bandwagon%2C%20leaving%20Sawant%20a%20bit%20wary%20about%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20prospects%20in%20meeting%20the%20target%20of%20winning%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20in%20the%20state%20in%20the%20coming%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESawant%20also%20announced%20that%20day%20that%20he%20would%20visit%20New%20Delhi%20on%20February%2016%20to%20press%20the%20BJP%20leadership%20to%20grant%20the%20demand.%20As%20planned%2C%20he%20met%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20on%20February%2019%20in%20Delhi.%20Shah%2C%20without%20spelling%20out%20any%20deadline%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fgoa%2Famit-shah-promises-to-resolve-st-quota-issue-for-polls-pramod-sawant%2Farticleshow%2F107816800.cms%5C%22%3Epromised%20to%20resolve%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%2024%2C%20Sawant%20met%20Shah%20again%2C%20this%20time%20with%20a%20sizeable%20delegation%20of%20leaders%20from%20the%20ST%20community.%20Once%20again%2C%20Shah%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.heraldgoa.in%2FGoa%2FCMled-delegation-meets-Amit-Shah-on-ST-reservation%2F218187%5C%22%3Eassured%20them%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9Cearly%20resolution%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fa%3E%20These%20ST%20leaders%20had%20by%20then%20declared%20that%20they%20would%20boycott%20the%202024%20elections%20if%20their%20demand%20was%20not%20met%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%202011%20census%2C%20Goa%E2%80%99s%20ST%20population%20was%20at%2010.23%25%2C%20which%20in%20the%20last%2013%20years%20may%20have%20gone%20up.%20The%20ST%20population%20is%20a%20decisive%20factor%20in%20the%20South%20Goa%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%20In%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20succeeded%20in%20increasing%20its%20country-wide%20tally%20from%20the%20one%20in%202014%2C%20it%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20win%20in%20South%20Goa.%20Former%20chief%20minister%20and%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20Francisco%20Sardinha%20had%20won%20the%20seat%20by%20a%20slim%20margin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20North%20Goa%20constituency%2C%20which%20the%20party%20won%20in%202019%2C%20also%20has%20significant%20numbers%20of%20ST%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20now%2C%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20not%20been%20able%20to%20placate%20the%20agitation%20leaders.%20According%20to%20news%20reports%2C%20they%20have%20rejected%20the%20decision%20since%20it%20is%20still%20a%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiscontent%20aside%2C%20if%20we%20look%20at%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20poll%20strategies%20aimed%20particularly%20at%20smaller%20communities%20which%20can%20be%20the%20deciding%20factor%20in%20just%20a%20fraction%20of%20assembly%20or%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%2C%20often%20the%20pattern%20is%20only%20to%20heap%20layer%20upon%20layer%20of%20promises%20to%20keep%20their%20hope%20tied%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBe%20it%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20promise%20since%20the%202014%20general%20elections%20to%20the%20Matua%20voters%20of%20Bengal%20(by%20promising%20them%20first%20to%20pass%20the%20Citizenship%20Amendment%20Bill%2C%20and%20then%20to%20implement%20the%20Act)%2C%20or%20to%20the%20Gorkha%2FNepali%20community%20particularly%20influential%20in%20the%20Darjeeling%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20(to%20grant%20them%20the%20Gorkhaland%20state)%2C%20the%20pattern%20is%20all%20too%20palpable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20agreement%20for%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Tripura%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20new%20front%2C%20based%20on%20this%20strategy%20of%20promises%20to%20a%20smaller%20group%20just%20before%20an%20election%2C%20has%20now%20been%20opened%20in%20Tripura%20by%20the%20Modi%20regime.%20The%20Modi-era%20BJP%2C%20which%20is%20now%20openly%20majoritarian%20in%20its%20approach%2C%20has%20been%20pussy-footing%20the%20demand%20for%20Greater%20Tipraland%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20minority%20ST%20community%20for%20some%20time%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20with%20the%202024%20elections%20looming%2C%20the%20tribal%20party%2C%20Tipra%20Motha%2C%20which%20is%20now%20the%20largest%20opposition%20in%20the%20state%20and%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20demand%2C%20announced%20that%20its%20leader%2C%20the%20well-recognised%20ex-royal%2C%20Pradyut%20Debbarma%2C%20would%20embark%20on%20a%20fast%20unto%20death%20protest%20to%20seek%20fulfilment%20of%20the%20demand.%20The%20party%20also%20began%20hobnobbing%20with%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20Opposition%20for%20a%20united%20fight%20in%20the%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20Goa%2C%20Tripura%20also%20has%20two%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%20While%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20majority%20Bengali%20population%20is%20the%20deciding%20factor%20in%20the%20West%20Tripura%20constituency%2C%20the%20East%20Tripura%20seat%20is%20reserved%20for%20the%20ST%20community.%20In%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20BJP%20had%20cornered%20the%20seat%20(along%20with%20the%20West%20Tripura%20seat)%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20verbal%20promise%20to%20the%20tribal%20leaders%20to%20look%20into%20the%20Tipraland%20demand.%20Lately%20though%2C%20the%20birth%20and%20meteoric%20rise%20of%20Tipra%20Motha%20which%20demanded%20no%20less%20than%20a%20written%20promise%20from%20the%20Modi-Shah%20regime%20on%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%2C%20made%20it%20an%20imperative%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20bring%20it%20to%20its%20side%2C%20lest%20the%20seat%20be%20won%20by%20the%20opposition%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%202%2C%20another%20express%20decision%20was%20made%20by%20the%20Modi%20government.%20It%20entered%20into%20a%20written%20agreement%20with%20Tipra%20Motha%20to%20settle%20the%20community%E2%80%99s%20demand%20for%20constitutional%20protection.%20Though%20a%20written%20promise%20has%20allowed%20the%20Tipra%20Motha%20to%20go%20to%20the%20community%20as%20a%20winner%2C%20in%20effect%2C%20it%20is%20not%20too%20different%20from%20the%20Goa%20promise.%20Both%20the%20promises%20are%20just%20that%20%E2%80%93%20a%20mere%20promise%20to%20look%20into%20the%20demands%20sometime%20in%20the%20future.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20moves%20urgently%20made%20by%20the%20government%20keeping%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20forthcoming%20electoral%20prospects%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%208%2C%20while%20the%20BJP%20has%20declared%20former%20Tripura%20chief%20minister%20Biplab%20Kumar%20Deb%20as%20its%20candidate%20from%20the%20West%20Tripura%20seat%2C%20it%20is%20yet%20to%20announce%20a%20candidate%20for%20the%20East%20Tripura%20seat%20%E2%80%93%20leaving%20political%20observers%20in%20the%20state%20to%20deduce%20that%20it%20would%20most%20likely%20be%20set%20aside%20for%20a%20consensus%20tribal%20candidate%20belonging%20to%20one%20of%20the%20parties%20aligned%20to%20the%20NDA%20including%20Tipra%20Motha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromises%20in%20Ladakh%20too%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Modi-Shah%20regime%20is%20likely%20to%20try%20the%20Goa-Tripura%20strategy%20in%20Ladakh%20too%2C%20to%20be%20able%20to%20retain%20the%20lone%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20the%20union%20territory%20(UT)%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnrest%20in%20the%20UT%20has%20been%20simmering%20for%20some%20time%20now.%20Led%20by%20local%20hero%20and%20climate%20activist%2C%20Sonam%20Wangchuk%2C%20the%20inspiration%20for%20Aamir%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20character%20in%20%3Cem%3E3%20Idiots%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20people%20have%20been%20seeking%20inclusion%20of%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20Sixth%20Schedule%20of%20the%20Constitution%20to%20protect%20their%20land%2C%20culture%20and%20environment.%20Wangchuk%20is%20currently%20on%20a%2021-day%20%E2%80%98climate%E2%80%99%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%204%2C%20a%20delegation%20of%20Ladakhi%20leaders%20seeking%20constitutional%20protection%20and%20statehood%20to%20Ladakh%20met%20Amit%20Shah%20but%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fno-positive-outcome-in-meeting-with-amit-shah-say-ladakh-bodies%2Farticle67913708.ece%5C%22%3Emeeting%20was%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20rounds%20of%20shutdowns%20have%20paralysed%20life%20in%20Leh-Ladakh%20in%20the%20last%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reports%2C%20Shah%20is%20likely%20to%20visit%20Ladakh%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20March%2C%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20make%20%E2%80%9Cpromises%E2%80%9D%20to%20match%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20Ladakhis.%20Quoting%20%E2%80%9Csources%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20March%202%20report%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fjammu-and-kashmir%2Fannouncement-on-parts-of-sixth-schedule-status-to-ladakh-during-home-minister-amit-shahs-visit-2919132%5C%22%3Ein%20the%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20Shah%20is%20likely%20to%20announce%20%E2%80%9Csome%20parts%20of%20Sixth%20Schedule%20status%20to%20the%20region%20during%20his%20visit%20later%20this%20month%E2%80%9D.%20The%20reference%20was%20to%20a%20report%20being%20readied%20by%20a%20high-powered%20committee%20set%20up%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20look%20into%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%9Csources%E2%80%9D%20told%20the%20newspaper%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20visit%20(of%20Shah)%20could%20happen%20either%20before%20the%20imposition%20of%20Model%20Code%20of%20Conduct%20(MCC)%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20or%20during%20the%20poll%20campaign.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20like%20in%20the%20STs%20of%20Tripura%20and%20Goa%2C%20a%20promise%20is%20in%20the%20offing%20for%20the%20STs%20of%20Ladakh%20too%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20clearly%20aiming%20at%20pocketing%20the%20lone%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromise%20in%20Gorkhaland%20too%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20poll-bound%20promises%2C%20the%20Gorkhas%2FNepalis%20of%20Darjeeling%20have%20to%20be%20appreciated%20the%20most%2C%20for%20their%20patience%20with%20the%20BJP.%20They%20have%20been%20continuously%20electing%20a%20BJP%20MP%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20the%20Darjeeling%20seat%20since%202009.%20In%202014%2C%20hopes%20rose%20particularly%20high%20because%20the%20party%2C%20with%20Modi%20as%20the%20prime%20ministerial%20candidate%2C%20promised%20Gorkhaland%20in%20its%20manifesto.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20no%20promises%20fulfilled%20by%20the%20party%20even%20after%20ten%20years%20of%20Modi%20rule%2C%20the%20Darjeeling%20areas%20have%20been%20witnessing%20angry%20protests%20of%20late.%20Sensing%20the%20public%20mood%2C%20the%20BJP%20Darjeeling%20MLA%20Neeraj%20Zimba%2C%20on%20March%203%2C%20had%20written%20a%20letter%20with%20his%20blood%20to%20Modi%2C%20reminding%20him%20that%20he%20had%20said%20%E2%80%9Cdreams%20of%20the%20Gorkhas%20are%20my%20dreams%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%2C%20while%20speaking%20at%20a%20public%20rally%20in%20neighbouring%20Siliguri%20this%20March%207%2C%20once%20again%20promised%20to%20keep%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20promise%20of%20Gorkhaland.%20Clearly%2C%20he%20is%20hoping%20that%20the%20patience%20of%20the%20Gorkhas%20can%20be%20tested%20in%202024%20too%20for%20the%20party%20to%20retain%20the%20Darjeeling%20seat%20this%20time.%20Like%20in%20Goa%20and%20Tripura%2C%20this%20promise%20is%20also%20an%20open-ended%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmplified%20protest%20in%20Eastern%20Nagaland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20BJP%20has%20not%20hesitated%20to%20repeat%20its%20promises%20to%20sets%20of%20voters%20in%20order%20to%20keep%20their%20hope%20going%2C%20the%20party%20is%20not%20in%20any%20hurry%20to%20fulfil%20at%20least%20one%20promise%20its%20Union%20government%20had%20made%20to%20a%20group%20of%20people%20in%20the%20Northeast.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20since%20early%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Eastern%20Nagaland%20People%E2%80%99s%20Organization%20(ENPO)%2C%20the%20outfit%20that%20has%20been%20spearheading%20the%20demand%20in%20six%20frontier%20districts%20of%20Nagaland%20for%20the%20Frontier%20Nagaland%20Territory%20(FNT)%2C%20has%20declared%20a%20%E2%80%98public%20emergency%E2%80%99%20and%20boycott%20of%20the%202024%20elections.%20No%20political%20party%20is%20to%20be%20allowed%20to%20even%20campaign%20in%20these%20districts%2C%20till%20the%20Modi-Shah%20regime%20fulfil%20its%20promise%20made%20to%20ENPO%20to%20carve%20out%20FNT%20from%20Nagaland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20promise%20had%20helped%20the%20BJP%20pocket%20several%20seats%20in%20the%20eastern%20Nagaland%20in%20the%202023%20assembly%20polls%2C%20making%20it%20the%20second%20largest%20in%20the%2060-member%20Nagaland%20assembly%20first%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20with%20Nagaland%20having%20only%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20ENPO%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20necessary%20weight%20to%20drive%20the%20Modi%20government%20towards%20making%20any%20move%20in%20its%20favour%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20general%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELike%20in%202019%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20already%20decided%20to%20put%20up%20a%20consensus%20NDA%20candidate%20for%20the%20Nagaland%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325832000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13131044%2FGINxSf5WcAAw8wr.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-the-flurry-of-bjps-sudden-promises-in-smaller-states-just-a-vote-catching-ploy%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20significant%20and%20rapid%20moves%20in%20Goa%20and%20Tripura%2C%20along%20with%20the%20hints%20it%20has%20dropped%20on%20Gorkhaland%2C%20betray%20a%20desperation%20to%20increase%20its%20electoral%20prospects.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A8%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fis-the-flurry-of-bjps-sudden-promises-in-smaller-states-just-a-vote-catching-ploy%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Assault%20on%20Navalny%20aide%20likely%20organised%20by%20Russia'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325654000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108464710%2Cimgsize-927455.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Feducation%2Ftimes-study-abroad%2Feurope%2Fassault-on-navalny-aide-likely-organised-by-russia-says-lithuanian-counter-intelligence%2Farticleshow%2F108463817.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F108463817.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ELeonid%20Volkov%2C%20a%20key%20aide%20to%20Alexei%20Navalny%2C%20was%20assaulted%20in%20Lithuania.%20The%20attack%2C%20orchestrated%20by%20Russia%2C%20involved%20tear%20gas%20and%20a%20hammer.%20The%20assault%20is%20likely%20linked%20to%20the%20Russian%20President%20election.%20Volkov%20posted%20images%20of%20his%20injuries%20and%20the%20vehicle%20damage%20on%20Telegram.%20The%20investigation%20is%20ongoing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Feducation%2Ftimes-study-abroad%2Feurope%2Fassault-on-navalny-aide-likely-organised-by-russia-says-lithuanian-counter-intelligence%2Farticleshow%2F108463817.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Feducation%2Ftimes-study-abroad%2Feurope%2Fassault-on-navalny-aide-likely-organised-by-russia-says-lithuanian-counter-intelligence%2Famp_articleshow%2F108463817.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fhome%2Feducation%2Ftimes-study-abroad%2Feurope%2Fassault-on-navalny-aide-likely-organised-by-russia-says-lithuanian-counter-intelligence%2Famp_articleshow%2F108463817.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lawyers%E2%80%99%20Body%20Urges%20CJI%20to%20Take%20Action%20Against%20UP%20Judge%20for%20Making%20Communal%20Remarks%20in%20Judgment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13145914%2FFYj9tb5UIAEsBYD.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20pan-India%20organisation%20of%20lawyers%20has%20written%20to%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20demanding%20action%20against%20a%20judge%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20who%2C%20while%20issuing%20an%20order%20in%20the%20trial%20of%20a%202010%20riots%20case%2C%20hailed%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20and%20blamed%20Muslims%20for%20communal%20riots%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20CJI%20Chandrachud%2C%20the%20All-India%20Lawyers%E2%80%99%20Association%20for%20Justice%20(AILAJ)%20also%20requested%20that%20the%20unnecessary%20observations%20made%20by%20judge%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%20in%20his%20March%205%20order%20be%20expunged%20from%20the%20record.%20AILAJ%20said%20judge%20Diwakar%E2%80%99s%20statements%20and%20conclusions%20in%20the%20order%20were%20%E2%80%9Ccontroversial%2C%20prejudicial%2C%20bigoted%20and%20unconstitutional.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyers%20body%20also%20accused%20judge%20Diwakar%20of%20displaying%20a%20%E2%80%9Csympathy%20for%20a%20majoritarian%20viewpoint%E2%80%9D%2C%20contrary%20to%20the%20duty%20to%20uphold%20the%20constitution%20and%20its%20fundamental%20values%2C%20and%20blatantly%20displaying%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdisregard%20for%20constitutional%20morality.%E2%80%9D%20This%20could%20not%20go%20unpunished%2C%20said%20the%20AILAJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiwakar%2C%20additional%20district%20judge-fast%20track%20court%20in%20Bareilly%2C%20on%20March%205%20%E2%80%93%20while%20invoking%20serious%20criminal%20charges%2C%20including%20attempt%20to%20murder%2C%20against%20prominent%20Muslim%20cleric-politician%20Maulana%20Tauqeer%20Raza%20Khan%2C%20for%20communal%20violence%20in%20Bareilly%20in%202010%20%E2%80%93%20hailed%20Adityanath%20as%20a%20great%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Creligious%20person%E2%80%9D%20occupying%20the%20seat%20of%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20order%2C%C2%A0judge%20Diwakar%2C%20who%20had%20earlier%20served%20in%20Varanasi%20and%20passed%20controversial%20orders%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20matter%2C%C2%A0made%C2%A0a%20string%20of%20seemingly%20controversial%20and%20debatable%20observations.%20Not%20only%20did%20he%20lavish%20Adityanath%20with%20praise%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20but%20he%20also%20blamed%20the%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cappeasement%E2%80%9D%20of%20a%20particular%20community%20(Muslims)%20by%20political%20parties%20for%20riots%20in%20the%20country%20and%20reflected%20on%20his%20own%20record%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20legal%20battle%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20and%20his%20family%20were%20living%20under%20fear%20after%20receiving%20threats%20from%20Muslim%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDiwakar%20described%20Adityanath%20as%20a%20modern-day%20example%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98philosopher%20king%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20concept%20of%20theocratic%20ruler%20propounded%20by%20ancient%20Greek%20philosopher%20Plato%20in%20his%20work%20%3Cem%3ERepublic%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20further%20remarked%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20reason%20for%20riots%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolitical%20parties%20here%20are%20engaged%20in%20appeasement%20of%20a%20particular%20religion.%E2%80%9D%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20the%20morale%20of%20prominent%20people%20of%20that%20%E2%80%9Cparticular%20religion%E2%80%9D%20increases%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20they%20believe%20that%20even%20if%20they%20cause%20riots%2C%20no%20harm%20will%20fall%20upon%20them%20due%20to%20protection%20provided%20by%20power%2C%20said%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AILAJ%20said%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20judge%20had%20the%20%E2%80%9Ceffect%20of%20perpetuating%20misplaced%20stereotypes%20and%20bigoted%20impressions%20about%20the%20Muslim%20community.%E2%80%9D%20In%20making%20these%20statements%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwhich%20reveal%20manifest%20bias%20and%20prejudice%20against%20the%20Muslim%C2%A0%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20judge%C2%A0failed%20the%20basic%20standards%20of%20judicial%20conduct%20thereby%20shaking%20the%20public%E2%80%99s%C2%A0confidence%20in%20the%20judiciary%2C%20said%20AILAJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6This%20order%20has%20tipped%20the%20scales%20of%20justice%2C%20breached%20the%20avowed%20principle%20of%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%20and%20is%20damaging%20to%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20judiciary.%20It%20represents%20an%20abject%20failure%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20Judge%20to%20abide%20by%20the%20standards%20and%20norms%20bearing%20on%20judicial%20officers%20i.e.%20to%20maintain%20independence%2C%20impartiality%20and%20propriety%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20AILAJ%20in%20its%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0AILAJ%20clarified%20that%20its%20objection%20was%20not%20in%20regard%20to%20the%20judicial%20order%2C%20but%20solely%20limited%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cexcessive%20and%20unnecessary%20obiter.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20the%202010%20Bareilly%20riots%20case%2C%20judge%20Diwakar%20added%20Khan%E2%80%99s%20name%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20and%20summoned%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20March%2011.%20Khan%20is%20a%20prominent%20cleric%20of%20the%20Barelvi%20sect%20and%20president%20of%20the%20political%20party%20Ittehad-e-Millat%20Council.%20The%20judge%20dubbed%20Khan%20as%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmain%20mastermind%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20riots%20that%20took%20place%20in%20Bareilly%20on%20March%202%2C%202010%2C%20after%20a%20dispute%20broke%20out%20over%20the%20route%20of%20a%20Muslim%20religious%20procession.%20Several%20persons%20were%20injured%20and%20properties%20damaged%20in%20the%20incident.%20A%20curfew%20had%20been%20imposed%20in%20the%20city%20for%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAILAJ%20also%20expressed%20objection%20to%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20direction%20that%20a%20copy%20of%20his%20order%20be%20sent%20to%20Adityanath%20so%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20could%20take%20action%20against%20those%20senior%20police%20officers%20and%20officials%20who%20allegedly%20assisted%20the%20accused%20Muslim%20cleric%20Khan%20and%20did%20not%20act%20as%20per%20law%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20then%20government.%20UP%20was%20then%20ruled%20by%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20led%20by%20Mayawati.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAny%20judicial%20order%20passed%20by%20the%20courts%20has%20an%20inescapable%20significance%2C%20not%20merely%20for%C2%A0the%20determination%20of%20inter%20se%20rights%2C%20but%20also%20for%20the%20impact%20it%20has%20on%20society%20and%20its%20views%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20AILAJ.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrevious%20judgements%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20serving%20as%20a%20judge%20in%20Varanasi%20in%202022%2C%20Diwakar%20had%20passed%20controversial%20directions%20regarding%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid.%20Diwakar%2C%20as%20civil%20judge%20senior%20division%2C%20had%20ordered%20the%20sealing%20of%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20Mughal-era%20Mosque%20after%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20claimed%20that%20a%20stone%20found%20in%20the%20ablution%20tank%20there%20was%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Eshivling%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudge%20Diwakar%20had%20given%20his%20nod%20to%20the%20videography%20inside%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Masjid%20by%20a%20court-appointed%20advocate%20commissioner%20on%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20five%20Hindu%20plaintiffs%20demanding%20daily%20access%20to%20prayer%20to%20an%20alleged%20Hindu%20side.%20%E2%80%98Maa%20Shringar%20Gauri%E2%80%99%2C%20they%20claimed%2C%20was%20located%20outside%20the%20western%20wall%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAILAJ%20requested%20the%20CJI%20to%20take%20necessary%20action%20against%20judge%20Diwakar%2C%20including%20skill%20development%20at%20the%20judicial%20academy.%20The%20lawyers%20body%20said%20that%20the%20judge%20met%20what%20the%20Supreme%20Curt%20had%20called%20%E2%80%9Cparameters%20for%20upgradation%20of%20skills.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20order%2C%20judge%20Diwakar%20had%20observed%20that%20if%20a%20religious%20person%20occupies%20a%20seat%20of%20power%2C%20it%20leads%20to%20good%20results.%20%E2%80%9CJustice%20is%20the%20lifeblood%20of%20a%20king%2C%E2%80%9Dsaid%20Diwakar%2C%20quickly%20adding%20that%20even%20though%2C%20in%20the%20present%20times%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98justice%E2%80%99%20was%20used%20in%20the%20legal%20sense%2C%20during%20the%20time%20of%20Plato%20it%20was%20used%20in%20the%20context%20of%20religion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20the%20head%20of%20power%20should%20be%20a%20religious%20person%2C%20because%20the%20life%20of%20a%20religious%20person%20is%20not%20one%20of%20enjoyment%20but%20of%20sacrifice%20and%20dedication.%20An%20example%20of%20this%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20times%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Epeethadeshwar%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20great%20Siddhapeeth%20Gorakhnath%20Temple%2C%20%3Cem%3Emahant%20baba%20shri%3C%2Fem%3E%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20ji%2C%20who%20is%20the%20current%20chief%20minister%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20has%20proven%20the%20above%20concept%20to%20be%20true%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20judge%20Diwakar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20however%2C%20if%20any%20religious%20person%20acts%20contrary%20to%20the%20aforementioned%2C%20such%20as%20provoking%20people%20of%20this%20community%2C%20then%20law%20and%20order%20gets%20disrupted%20and%20riots%20occur%2C%20said%20the%20judge.%20Diwakar%20said%20an%20example%20of%20this%20was%20Maulana%20Khan.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710325123000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2F13145914%2FFYj9tb5UIAEsBYD.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flawyers-body-urges-cji-to-take-action-against-up-judge-for-making-communal-remarks-in-judgment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Judge%20Ravi%20Kumar%20Diwakar%20hailed%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20his%20religious%20background%20and%20blamed%20Muslims%20for%20communal%20riots%20in%20the%20country%20while%20passing%20an%20order%20in%20a%202010%20riot%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Flawyers-body-urges-cji-to-take-action-against-up-judge-for-making-communal-remarks-in-judgment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20pause%20on%20funding%20UN%20relief%20agency%20for%20Palestinians%20may%20become%20permanent%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1710324027000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-108463026%2Cimgsize-1522021.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.