oreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F82739%2Fifarm-integrated-aquaponics-poultry-kerala-veterinary-university%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20fish%20tanks.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20nitrates%20produced%20by%20fish%20waste%2C%20he%20also%20adds%20iron%20nails%2C%20lime%20and%20egg%20shells%20to%20increase%20the%20iron%20and%20calcium%20nutrients.%20After%20six%20months%20of%20research%20and%20assistance%20from%20ICAR-CAFRI%2C%20he%20successfully%20grew%20vegetables%20in%20a%20600%20sq%20ft%20area%20for%20three%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202018%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20quit%20his%20job%20and%20grow%20vegetables%20in%20a%20commercial%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F343071%2Fhow-to-grow-strawberries-dragon-fruit-turmeric-terrace-gardening%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eterrace%20setup.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresently%2C%20he%20grows%20nearly%202%2C500%20varieties%20of%20plants%2C%20which%20include%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20medicinal%20herbs%2C%20and%20flowers%20and%20harvests%20500%20kg%20of%20vegetables%20every%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFound%20his%20work%20interesting%3F%20Watch%20this%20short%20video%20to%20find%20out%20more%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Ftp3W87JX0ps%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3D